UPDATE BookPuzzles SET HintsJson='{"de":["Ein Springertausch räumt den Weg für den durchlaufenden Freibauern.","Der eigene Springer und der Randbauer arbeiten zusammen zur Umwandlung.","Springer nach b5 – leitet die siegreiche Folge ein."],"en":["A knight trade clears the path for the runaway passed pawn.","Your knight and the rook''s-file pawn combine to promote.","Knight to b5 — beginning the winning sequence."],"hr":["Zamjena skakača otvara put odbjeglom slobodnom pješaku.","Tvoj skakač i rubni pješak surađuju do promocije.","Skakač na b5 — pokreće pobjednički niz."]}', HintsVersion=1 WHERE LineId LIKE '%:009.088' AND BookFileName='chessable-u5-21646.pgn';
UPDATE BookPuzzles SET HintsJson='{"de":["Der Springer wird geopfert, um dem Freibauern die Bahn zur Dame zu öffnen.","Springer und Randbauer ebnen gemeinsam den Weg zur Umwandlung.","Springer nach f8 – startet die entscheidende Kombination."],"en":["The knight is sacrificed to clear the passer''s road to a new queen.","Knight and rook''s-pawn together pave the way to promotion.","Knight to f8 — starting the decisive combination."],"hr":["Skakač se žrtvuje da otvori put slobodnom pješaku do nove dame.","Skakač i rubni pješak zajedno krče put do promocije.","Skakač na f8 — započinje odlučujuću kombinaciju."]}', HintsVersion=1 WHERE LineId LIKE '%:009.089' AND BookFileName='chessable-u5-21646.pgn';
UPDATE BookPuzzles SET HintsJson='{"de":["Ein Springermanöver fängt den feindlichen Springer und sichert den entscheidenden Vorteil.","Der eigene Springer tanzt zur Gabel und erbeutet die gegnerische Figur.","Springer nach c1 – beginnt die figurengewinnende Kombination."],"en":["A knight maneuver traps the enemy knight and secures a decisive edge.","Your knight dances into a fork and wins the opposing piece.","Knight to c1 — starting the piece-winning combination."],"hr":["Manevar skakača hvata protivničkog skakača i osigurava odlučujuću prednost.","Tvoj skakač pleše do viljuške i osvaja protivničku figuru.","Skakač na c1 — započinje kombinaciju koja dobiva figuru."]}', HintsVersion=1 WHERE LineId LIKE '%:009.090' AND BookFileName='chessable-u5-21646.pgn';
UPDATE BookPuzzles SET HintsJson='{"de":["Ein Turmopfer öffnet dem zentralen Freibauern den Weg zur Umwandlung.","Turm und Läufer geleiten den durchlaufenden Bauern bis ins Damenfeld.","Turm schlägt auf g6 – leitet die siegreiche Folge ein."],"en":["A rook sacrifice opens the road for the central passer to promote.","Rook and bishop escort the runaway pawn all the way to queening.","Rook takes on g6 — beginning the winning sequence."],"hr":["Žrtva topa otvara put središnjem slobodnjaku do promocije.","Top i lovac prate odbjeglog pješaka sve do polja dame.","Top uzima na g6 — pokreće pobjednički niz."]}', HintsVersion=1 WHERE LineId LIKE '%:009.091' AND BookFileName='chessable-u5-21646.pgn';
UPDATE BookPuzzles SET HintsJson='{"de":["Ein Zwischenschach gewinnt Tempo und ebnet dem Bauern den Weg zur Dame.","Der Läufer gibt mit Tempo Schach, dann läuft der Freibauer durch.","Läufer nach e3 – das tempogewinnende Zwischenschach vor dem Bauerndurchbruch."],"en":["An in-between check gains a tempo and clears the pawn''s road to a queen.","The bishop checks with tempo, then the passer runs through.","Bishop to e3 — the tempo-gaining zwischenzug before the pawn breaks through."],"hr":["Međušah dobiva tempo i otvara pješaku put do dame.","Lovac daje šah s tempom, a zatim slobodnjak prolazi.","Lovac na e3 — međušah s tempom prije proboja pješaka."]}', HintsVersion=1 WHERE LineId LIKE '%:009.092' AND BookFileName='chessable-u5-21646.pgn';
UPDATE BookPuzzles SET HintsJson='{"de":["Ein Turmopfer entblößt den König und führt zu entscheidendem Materialgewinn.","Die Läufer übernehmen die Diagonalen und kassieren nach dem Opfer ab.","Turm schlägt auf f7 – beginnt die entscheidende Kombination."],"en":["A rook sacrifice strips the king and leads to decisive material gain.","The bishops seize the diagonals and cash in after the sacrifice.","Rook takes on f7 — starting the decisive combination."],"hr":["Žrtva topa ogoljuje kralja i vodi do odlučujuće materijalne prednosti.","Lovci preuzimaju dijagonale i naplaćuju nakon žrtve.","Top uzima na f7 — započinje odlučujuću kombinaciju."]}', HintsVersion=1 WHERE LineId LIKE '%:009.093' AND BookFileName='chessable-u5-21646.pgn';
UPDATE BookPuzzles SET HintsJson='{"de":["Ein Bauernopfer lenkt den König weg und lässt den Freibauern durchlaufen.","Der durchgebrochene Bauer und der Läufer entscheiden gemeinsam.","Bauer nach c3 – das ablenkende Opfer vor dem entscheidenden Vormarsch."],"en":["A pawn sacrifice deflects the king and lets the passer run free.","The breakthrough pawn and the bishop decide the game together.","Pawn to c3 — the deflecting sacrifice before the decisive advance."],"hr":["Žrtva pješaka odvlači kralja i pušta slobodnjaka da slobodno trči.","Probojni pješak i lovac zajedno odlučuju partiju.","Pješak na c3 — žrtva odvlačenja prije odlučujućeg prodora."]}', HintsVersion=1 WHERE LineId LIKE '%:009.094' AND BookFileName='chessable-u5-21646.pgn';
UPDATE BookPuzzles SET HintsJson='{"de":["Der Freibauer wird vorbereitet, während Turm und Springer den Vormarsch stützen.","Springer und Turm koordinieren, um dem Bauern die Bahn freizuhalten.","Bauer nach c2 – beginnt die siegreiche Bauernfolge."],"en":["The passer is readied while rook and knight support its advance.","Knight and rook coordinate to keep the pawn''s path open.","Pawn to c2 — beginning the winning pawn sequence."],"hr":["Slobodnjak se priprema dok ga top i skakač podupiru u prodoru.","Skakač i top surađuju da pješaku drže put otvorenim.","Pješak na c2 — pokreće pobjednički pješački niz."]}', HintsVersion=1 WHERE LineId LIKE '%:009.095' AND BookFileName='chessable-u5-21646.pgn';
UPDATE BookPuzzles SET HintsJson='{"de":["Eine Räumung schafft Platz und treibt den Freibauern zur Umwandlung.","Läufer und Bauer arbeiten zusammen, um die Diagonale zu öffnen und durchzubrechen.","König nach e8 – leitet die entscheidende Folge ein."],"en":["A clearance makes room and drives the passer toward promotion.","Bishop and pawn work together to open the diagonal and break through.","King to e8 — beginning the decisive sequence."],"hr":["Čišćenje polja stvara prostor i tjera slobodnjaka prema promociji.","Lovac i pješak surađuju da otvore dijagonalu i probiju se.","Kralj na e8 — započinje odlučujući niz."]}', HintsVersion=1 WHERE LineId LIKE '%:009.096' AND BookFileName='chessable-u5-21646.pgn';
UPDATE BookPuzzles SET HintsJson='{"de":["Eine Reihe von Opfern lockt die weißen Figuren weg und der Bauer wird Dame.","Läufer und der vorgerückte Bauer wirken zusammen bis zur Umwandlung.","Läufer nach e5 – beginnt die siegreiche Opferfolge."],"en":["A chain of sacrifices lures the white pieces away and the pawn queens.","Bishop and the advanced pawn act together to reach promotion.","Bishop to e5 — beginning the winning sacrificial sequence."],"hr":["Niz žrtava odvlači bijele figure i pješak postaje dama.","Lovac i napredni pješak djeluju zajedno do promocije.","Lovac na e5 — započinje pobjednički niz žrtava."]}', HintsVersion=1 WHERE LineId LIKE '%:009.097' AND BookFileName='chessable-u5-21646.pgn';
UPDATE BookPuzzles SET HintsJson='{"de":["Ein Turmmanöver bändigt die gegnerischen Figuren und sichert die Umwandlung.","Turm und Läufer schirmen den Freibauern auf seinem Weg zur Dame ab.","Turm nach g4 – leitet die entscheidende Folge ein."],"en":["A rook maneuver tames the enemy pieces and secures the promotion.","Rook and bishop shield the passer on its way to a new queen.","Rook to g4 — beginning the decisive sequence."],"hr":["Manevar topa obuzdava protivničke figure i osigurava promociju.","Top i lovac štite slobodnjaka na putu do nove dame.","Top na g4 — započinje odlučujući niz."]}', HintsVersion=1 WHERE LineId LIKE '%:009.098' AND BookFileName='chessable-u5-21646.pgn';
UPDATE BookPuzzles SET HintsJson='{"de":["Mehrere Ablenkungsopfer bahnen dem Freibauern den Weg zur Dame.","Dame und Läufer beseitigen die Verteidiger, dann läuft der Bauer durch.","Turm schlägt auf f7 – beginnt die siegreiche Kombination."],"en":["Several deflecting sacrifices clear the passer''s path to a new queen.","Queen and bishop remove the defenders, then the pawn runs through.","Rook takes on f7 — beginning the winning combination."],"hr":["Nekoliko žrtava odvlačenja krči slobodnjaku put do nove dame.","Dama i lovac uklanjaju branitelje, a zatim pješak prolazi.","Top uzima na f7 — započinje pobjedničku kombinaciju."]}', HintsVersion=1 WHERE LineId LIKE '%:009.099' AND BookFileName='chessable-u5-21646.pgn';
UPDATE BookPuzzles SET HintsJson='{"de":["Trotz gewaltiger Übermacht steckst du fest – nur das Dauerschach rettet das Remis.","Die Dame jagt den feindlichen König ohne Entkommen und erzwingt die Punkteteilung.","Dame schlägt auf g1 – beginnt die rettende Schachfolge zum Remis."],"en":["Despite huge force you are stuck — only perpetual check saves the draw.","The queen hounds the enemy king with no escape and forces the split.","Queen takes on g1 — beginning the saving checking sequence for the draw."],"hr":["Unatoč golemoj nadmoći zaglavio si — samo vječni šah spašava remi.","Dama goni protivničkog kralja bez bijega i prisiljava podjelu boda.","Dama uzima na g1 — započinje spasonosni niz šahova za remi."]}', HintsVersion=1 WHERE LineId LIKE '%:010.003' AND BookFileName='chessable-u5-21646.pgn';
UPDATE BookPuzzles SET HintsJson='{"de":["Der Läufer droht zu einem theoretisch toten Endspiel zu vereinfachen – nur so hältst du Remis.","Läufer und König grenzen den feindlichen Monarchen ein und halten die Stellung.","Läufer nach d5 – startet das rettende Manöver zum Remis."],"en":["The bishop threatens to liquidate into a theoretically dead ending — your only save.","Bishop and king box in the enemy monarch and hold the position.","Bishop to d5 — starting the saving maneuver to the draw."],"hr":["Lovac prijeti pojednostavljenjem u teorijski mrtvu završnicu — to ti je jedini spas.","Lovac i kralj zatvaraju protivničkog vladara i drže poziciju.","Lovac na d5 — započinje spasonosni manevar do remija."]}', HintsVersion=1 WHERE LineId LIKE '%:010.004' AND BookFileName='chessable-u5-21646.pgn';
UPDATE BookPuzzles SET HintsJson='{"de":["Du stehst schlechter und musst dich mit Dauerschach ins Remis retten.","Die Dame muss den weißen König unaufhörlich verfolgen, sonst geht es verloren.","Dame nach e3 – das Schach, das die rettende Dauerschachfolge eröffnet."],"en":["You are worse and must rescue a draw by perpetual check.","The queen must chase the white king relentlessly or the game is lost.","Queen to e3 — the check that opens the saving perpetual."],"hr":["Stojiš lošije i moraš se spasiti remijem vječnim šahom.","Dama mora neprestano goniti bijelog kralja, inače je izgubljeno.","Dama na e3 — šah koji otvara spasonosni vječni šah."]}', HintsVersion=1 WHERE LineId LIKE '%:010.005' AND BookFileName='chessable-u5-21646.pgn';
UPDATE BookPuzzles SET HintsJson='{"de":["Statt des feindlichen Damebauern droht Patt oder Dauerschach – nur so entkommst du dem Verlust.","Die Dame klammert sich an den König und sucht das rettende Dauerschach.","Dame nach c2 – startet die rettende Schachjagd zum Remis."],"en":["Against the enemy passer only perpetual check or stalemate tricks save you.","The queen clings to the king, hunting the saving perpetual.","Queen to c2 — starting the saving checking chase for the draw."],"hr":["Protiv protivničkog slobodnjaka spašava te samo vječni šah ili pat-trik.","Dama se prilijepi za kralja tražeći spasonosni vječni šah.","Dama na c2 — započinje spasonosnu hajku šahovima za remi."]}', HintsVersion=1 WHERE LineId LIKE '%:010.007' AND BookFileName='chessable-u5-21646.pgn';
UPDATE BookPuzzles SET HintsJson='{"de":["Du musst ins Remis flüchten – ein Dauerschach des Turms ist die Rettung.","Der Turm pendelt unermüdlich und lässt dem feindlichen König keine Ruhe.","Turm nach d2 – beginnt das rettende Dauerschach."],"en":["You must escape into a draw — a rook perpetual is the rescue.","The rook shuttles tirelessly and gives the enemy king no peace.","Rook to d2 — beginning the saving perpetual check."],"hr":["Moraš pobjeći u remi — vječni šah topom je spas.","Top neumorno njiše i ne da protivničkom kralju mira.","Top na d2 — započinje spasonosni vječni šah."]}', HintsVersion=1 WHERE LineId LIKE '%:010.008' AND BookFileName='chessable-u5-21646.pgn';
UPDATE BookPuzzles SET HintsJson='{"de":["Ein Damenopfer leitet ein rettendes Dauerschach ein, das das Remis sichert.","Nach dem Damenopfer übernimmt der Turm die unaufhörliche Schachjagd.","Dame schlägt auf g2 – das Opfer, das das rettende Dauerschach eröffnet."],"en":["A queen sacrifice ushers in a saving perpetual that secures the draw.","After the queen sac the rook takes over the endless checking.","Queen takes on g2 — the sacrifice that opens the saving perpetual."],"hr":["Žrtva dame uvodi spasonosni vječni šah koji osigurava remi.","Nakon žrtve dame top preuzima neprestanu hajku šahovima.","Dama uzima na g2 — žrtva koja otvara spasonosni vječni šah."]}', HintsVersion=1 WHERE LineId LIKE '%:010.009' AND BookFileName='chessable-u5-21646.pgn';
UPDATE BookPuzzles SET HintsJson='{"de":["Ein Damenopfer reißt die Königsstellung auf und mündet in rettendes Dauerschach.","Nach dem Opfer jagt der Turm den entblößten König ins Remis.","Dame schlägt auf g7 – das Opfer, das das rettende Dauerschach einleitet."],"en":["A queen sacrifice tears open the king''s cover and leads to a saving perpetual.","After the sac the rook chases the exposed king into a draw.","Queen takes on g7 — the sacrifice that begins the saving perpetual."],"hr":["Žrtva dame razbija kraljevo zaklonište i vodi do spasonosnog vječnog šaha.","Nakon žrtve top goni izloženog kralja u remi.","Dama uzima na g7 — žrtva koja započinje spasonosni vječni šah."]}', HintsVersion=1 WHERE LineId LIKE '%:010.010' AND BookFileName='chessable-u5-21646.pgn';
UPDATE BookPuzzles SET HintsJson='{"de":["Ein Opfer erzwingt ein Dauerschach der Dame und hält das Remis.","Die Dame pendelt zwischen zwei Feldern und lässt dem König kein Entkommen.","Turm nach a8 – das Opfer, das das rettende Dauerschach eröffnet."],"en":["A sacrifice forces a queen perpetual and holds the draw.","The queen oscillates between two squares with no escape for the king.","Rook to a8 — the sacrifice that opens the saving perpetual."],"hr":["Žrtva prisiljava vječni šah damom i drži remi.","Dama njiše između dva polja bez bijega za kralja.","Top na a8 — žrtva koja otvara spasonosni vječni šah."]}', HintsVersion=1 WHERE LineId LIKE '%:010.011' AND BookFileName='chessable-u5-21646.pgn';
UPDATE BookPuzzles SET HintsJson='{"de":["Ein Turmopfer öffnet die Linie für das rettende Dauerschach der Dame.","Nach dem Opfer jagt die Dame den König ewig hin und her.","Turm schlägt auf c6 – das Opfer, das das rettende Dauerschach einleitet."],"en":["A rook sacrifice opens the line for the queen''s saving perpetual.","After the sac the queen chases the king back and forth forever.","Rook takes on c6 — the sacrifice that begins the saving perpetual."],"hr":["Žrtva topa otvara liniju za spasonosni vječni šah damom.","Nakon žrtve dama vječno goni kralja amo-tamo.","Top uzima na c6 — žrtva koja započinje spasonosni vječni šah."]}', HintsVersion=1 WHERE LineId LIKE '%:010.012' AND BookFileName='chessable-u5-21646.pgn';
UPDATE BookPuzzles SET HintsJson='{"de":["Ein Vorstoß droht und sichert dem Turm ein rettendes Dauerschach.","Der Turm pendelt auf der Linie und hält das Remis am Leben.","Bauer nach a7 – startet das rettende Dauerschach."],"en":["An advance threatens and earns the rook a saving perpetual.","The rook shuttles along the file and keeps the draw alive.","Pawn to a7 — starting the saving perpetual check."],"hr":["Prodor prijeti i osigurava topu spasonosni vječni šah.","Top njiše po liniji i održava remi na životu.","Pješak na a7 — započinje spasonosni vječni šah."]}', HintsVersion=1 WHERE LineId LIKE '%:010.013' AND BookFileName='chessable-u5-21646.pgn';
UPDATE BookPuzzles SET HintsJson='{"de":["Ein Doppelschach erzwingt das Remis statt Materialgewinn oder Matt.","Der Turm gibt das Schach, das den König ewig hin- und herzieht.","Turm nach f1 – das Doppelschach, das das rettende Dauerschach eröffnet."],"en":["A double check forces the draw instead of winning material or mating.","The rook delivers the check that drags the king to and fro forever.","Rook to f1 — the double check that opens the saving perpetual."],"hr":["Dvostruki šah prisiljava remi umjesto dobitka materijala ili mata.","Top daje šah koji vječno povlači kralja amo-tamo.","Top na f1 — dvostruki šah koji otvara spasonosni vječni šah."]}', HintsVersion=1 WHERE LineId LIKE '%:010.014' AND BookFileName='chessable-u5-21646.pgn';
UPDATE BookPuzzles SET HintsJson='{"de":["Der Turm jagt den König unermüdlich und rettet das Remis durch Dauerschach.","Der Turm pendelt zwischen den Feldern, bis der König nicht mehr entkommt.","Turm nach b1 – beginnt das rettende Dauerschach."],"en":["The rook hounds the king tirelessly and saves the draw by perpetual.","The rook shuttles between squares until the king can no longer escape.","Rook to b1 — beginning the saving perpetual check."],"hr":["Top neumorno goni kralja i spašava remi vječnim šahom.","Top njiše među poljima dok kralj više ne može pobjeći.","Top na b1 — započinje spasonosni vječni šah."]}', HintsVersion=1 WHERE LineId LIKE '%:010.015' AND BookFileName='chessable-u5-21646.pgn';
UPDATE BookPuzzles SET HintsJson='{"de":["Die Dame zwingt den König in ein ewiges Schach und hält das Remis.","Die Dame pendelt unaufhörlich und lässt dem feindlichen König keine Ruhe.","Dame nach h8 – beginnt das rettende Dauerschach."],"en":["The queen forces the king into an endless check and holds the draw.","The queen oscillates relentlessly, giving the enemy king no peace.","Queen to h8 — beginning the saving perpetual check."],"hr":["Dama tjera kralja u vječni šah i drži remi.","Dama neprestano njiše i ne da protivničkom kralju mira.","Dama na h8 — započinje spasonosni vječni šah."]}', HintsVersion=1 WHERE LineId LIKE '%:010.016' AND BookFileName='chessable-u5-21646.pgn';
UPDATE BookPuzzles SET HintsJson='{"de":["Ein Damenopfer leitet ein Dauerschach des Springers ein und rettet das Remis.","Nach dem Opfer hüpft der Springer in ein nicht endendes Schach.","Dame schlägt auf f3 – das Opfer, das das rettende Dauerschach eröffnet."],"en":["A queen sacrifice ushers in a knight perpetual and saves the draw.","After the sac the knight hops into a never-ending check.","Queen takes on f3 — the sacrifice that opens the saving perpetual."],"hr":["Žrtva dame uvodi vječni šah skakačem i spašava remi.","Nakon žrtve skakač uskače u beskonačni šah.","Dama uzima na f3 — žrtva koja otvara spasonosni vječni šah."]}', HintsVersion=1 WHERE LineId LIKE '%:010.017' AND BookFileName='chessable-u5-21646.pgn';
UPDATE BookPuzzles SET HintsJson='{"de":["Ein Turmopfer befreit den Springer für ein rettendes Dauerschach.","Nach dem Opfer hüpft der Springer in ein ewiges Schach.","Turm nach e8 – das Opfer, das das rettende Dauerschach einleitet."],"en":["A rook sacrifice frees the knight for a saving perpetual check.","After the sac the knight hops into an everlasting check.","Rook to e8 — the sacrifice that begins the saving perpetual."],"hr":["Žrtva topa oslobađa skakača za spasonosni vječni šah.","Nakon žrtve skakač uskače u vječni šah.","Top na e8 — žrtva koja započinje spasonosni vječni šah."]}', HintsVersion=1 WHERE LineId LIKE '%:010.018' AND BookFileName='chessable-u5-21646.pgn';
UPDATE BookPuzzles SET HintsJson='{"de":["Eine Unterverwandlung in einen Springer sichert überraschend das Remis.","Der neue Springer hüpft hin und her und erzwingt das Dauerschach.","Bauer wandelt auf g8 in einen Springer um – beginnt das rettende Dauerschach."],"en":["An underpromotion to a knight surprisingly secures the draw.","The new knight hops back and forth and forces the perpetual.","Pawn promotes to a knight on g8 — beginning the saving perpetual."],"hr":["Slaba promocija u skakača iznenađujuće osigurava remi.","Novi skakač skače amo-tamo i prisiljava vječni šah.","Pješak na g8 promovira u skakača — započinje spasonosni vječni šah."]}', HintsVersion=1 WHERE LineId LIKE '%:010.019' AND BookFileName='chessable-u5-21646.pgn';
UPDATE BookPuzzles SET HintsJson='{"de":["Ein Opfer ebnet den Weg zu einem rettenden Dauerschach des Turms.","Turm und König wirken zusammen, um das ewige Schach zu erzwingen.","Bauer schlägt auf g3 – das Opfer, das das rettende Dauerschach einleitet."],"en":["A sacrifice paves the way to a saving rook perpetual.","Rook and king cooperate to force the endless check.","Pawn takes on g3 — the sacrifice that begins the saving perpetual."],"hr":["Žrtva krči put do spasonosnog vječnog šaha topom.","Top i kralj surađuju da prisile beskonačni šah.","Pješak uzima na g3 — žrtva koja započinje spasonosni vječni šah."]}', HintsVersion=1 WHERE LineId LIKE '%:010.020' AND BookFileName='chessable-u5-21646.pgn';
UPDATE BookPuzzles SET HintsJson='{"de":["Du stehst unter Druck, doch ein endloser Schachschauer rettet das Remis.","Deine Dame jagt den feindlichen König und kommt nie zur Ruhe.","Dame schlägt auf f2 – der Auftakt zum rettenden Dauerschach."],"en":["You are under pressure, but a never-ending stream of checks saves the draw.","Your queen hunts the enemy king and never lets him rest.","Queen takes on f2 — the start of the saving perpetual."],"hr":["Pod pritiskom si, no beskrajna kiša šahova spašava remi.","Tvoja dama lovi protivničkog kralja i ne da mu predahnuti.","Dama uzima na f2 — početak spasonosnog vječitog šaha."]}', HintsVersion=1 WHERE LineId LIKE '%:010.021' AND BookFileName='chessable-u5-21646.pgn';
UPDATE BookPuzzles SET HintsJson='{"de":["Du musst das Remis durch ewiges Schachgeben sichern.","Der Springer hüpft um den König und lässt ihn nicht entkommen.","Springer nach h3 – Beginn des rettenden Dauerschachs."],"en":["You must secure the draw with endless checks.","The knight dances around the king and never lets him escape.","Knight to h3 — the start of the saving perpetual."],"hr":["Remi moraš osigurati neprekidnim šahovima.","Skakač skače oko kralja i ne da mu pobjeći.","Skakač na h3 — početak spasonosnog vječitog šaha."]}', HintsVersion=1 WHERE LineId LIKE '%:010.022' AND BookFileName='chessable-u5-21646.pgn';
UPDATE BookPuzzles SET HintsJson='{"de":["Aus der Bedrängnis hilft nur das Dauerschach zum Remis.","Turm und Dame wechseln sich beim Schachgeben ab.","Turm nach e1 – der Auftakt zum rettenden Dauerschach."],"en":["Only a perpetual rescues the draw from your trouble.","Rook and queen take turns delivering the checks.","Rook to e1 — the start of the saving perpetual."],"hr":["Iz nevolje te spašava samo vječiti šah za remi.","Top i dama izmjenjuju se u davanju šaha.","Top na e1 — početak spasonosnog vječitog šaha."]}', HintsVersion=1 WHERE LineId LIKE '%:010.023' AND BookFileName='chessable-u5-21646.pgn';
UPDATE BookPuzzles SET HintsJson='{"de":["Rette dich mit unermüdlichem Schachgeben ins Remis.","Der Turm pendelt am König und gönnt ihm keine Ruhe.","Turm nach g1 – Beginn des rettenden Dauerschachs."],"en":["Save yourself into a draw with relentless checks.","The rook shuttles beside the king and gives him no rest.","Rook to g1 — the start of the saving perpetual."],"hr":["Spasi se u remi nemilosrdnim šahovima.","Top njiše uz kralja i ne da mu mira.","Top na g1 — početak spasonosnog vječitog šaha."]}', HintsVersion=1 WHERE LineId LIKE '%:010.024' AND BookFileName='chessable-u5-21646.pgn';
UPDATE BookPuzzles SET HintsJson='{"de":["Nur Dauerschach hält die Partie für dich im Remis.","Der Turm verfolgt den König unaufhörlich.","Turm nach e1 – der Auftakt zum rettenden Dauerschach."],"en":["Only a perpetual keeps the game level for you.","The rook chases the king without pause.","Rook to e1 — the start of the saving perpetual."],"hr":["Samo vječiti šah drži partiju u remiju za tebe.","Top neprestano progoni kralja.","Top na e1 — početak spasonosnog vječitog šaha."]}', HintsVersion=1 WHERE LineId LIKE '%:010.025' AND BookFileName='chessable-u5-21646.pgn';
