UPDATE BookPuzzles SET HintsJson='{"de":["Mit einer geschickten Bauernkette lockst du eine schwere Figur ins Verderben und gewinnst Material.","Der vorrückende Freibauer und ein Turm zwingen den gegnerischen Turm in eine fatale Lage.","Bauer nach c5 – beginnt die Kombination, die einen Turm fängt."],"en":["A clever pawn advance lures a heavy piece to its doom and wins material.","The marching passed pawn and a rook drive the enemy rook into a trap.","Pawn to c5 — starts the combination that traps a rook."],"hr":["Vješt potez pješakom mami tešku figuru u propast i osvaja materijal.","Prodorni slobodnjak i top tjeraju protivnički top u zamku.","Pješak na c5 — započinje kombinaciju koja hvata top."]}', HintsVersion=1 WHERE LineId LIKE '%:013.050' AND BookFileName='chessable-u5-21646.pgn';
UPDATE BookPuzzles SET HintsJson='{"de":["Ein Schlagopfer reißt die Verteidigung des Mattfeldes weg und gewinnt entscheidend.","Erst weicht die Verteidigung der Grundreihe, dann holt deine Dame die gefesselte Figur.","Turm nimmt auf f1 – leitet die gewinnbringende Folge ein."],"en":["A sacrifice tears away the guard of the mating square and wins decisively.","First the back-rank defence is removed, then your queen collects the pinned piece.","Rook takes on f1 — begins the winning sequence."],"hr":["Žrtva uklanja čuvara matnog polja i odlučujuće pobjeđuje.","Najprije pada obrana zadnjeg reda, zatim dama uzima vezanu figuru.","Top uzima na f1 — započinje dobitni niz."]}', HintsVersion=1 WHERE LineId LIKE '%:013.051' AND BookFileName='chessable-u5-21646.pgn';
UPDATE BookPuzzles SET HintsJson='{"de":["Vorsicht: ein scheinbarer Angriff erlaubt dem Gegner eine Gabel, die Material gewinnt.","Nach dem Rückzug des Turms steht ein Schläger bereit, der Läufer und Dame gleichzeitig trifft.","Dame nimmt auf f5 – doch der Gegner gabelt und gewinnt."],"en":["Beware: a tempting attack lets the opponent fork and win material.","After the rook steps aside, a piece is poised to hit bishop and queen at once.","Queen takes on f5 — but the reply forks and wins."],"hr":["Oprez: primamljiv napad omogućuje protivniku vilicu koja osvaja materijal.","Nakon povlačenja topa, figura prijeti istovremeno lovcu i dami.","Dama uzima na f5 — no protivnik vilicom pobjeđuje."]}', HintsVersion=1 WHERE LineId LIKE '%:013.052' AND BookFileName='chessable-u5-21646.pgn';
UPDATE BookPuzzles SET HintsJson='{"de":["Ein Schlagopfer öffnet die Stellung und führt zu entscheidendem Materialgewinn.","Turm und Dame arbeiten zusammen, um die feindliche Dame zu fangen.","Turm nimmt auf f5 – beginnt die gewinnende Kombination."],"en":["A sacrifice rips open the position and leads to decisive material gain.","Rook and queen combine to snare the enemy queen.","Rook takes on f5 — starts the winning combination."],"hr":["Žrtva otvara poziciju i vodi do odlučujuće materijalne prednosti.","Top i dama surađuju kako bi uhvatili protivničku damu.","Top uzima na f5 — započinje dobitnu kombinaciju."]}', HintsVersion=1 WHERE LineId LIKE '%:013.053' AND BookFileName='chessable-u5-21646.pgn';
UPDATE BookPuzzles SET HintsJson='{"de":["Ein erzwungenes Matt liegt in der Luft.","Ein Schlagopfer öffnet den König, dann setzen Springer und Dame nach.","Turm nimmt auf c8 – erzwingt das Matt."],"en":["A forced mate is in the air.","A sacrifice exposes the king, then knight and queen close in.","Rook takes on c8 — forces the mate."],"hr":["Prisilni mat visi u zraku.","Žrtva razgolićuje kralja, zatim skakač i dama nastupaju.","Top uzima na c8 — prisiljava mat."]}', HintsVersion=1 WHERE LineId LIKE '%:013.054' AND BookFileName='chessable-u5-21646.pgn';
UPDATE BookPuzzles SET HintsJson='{"de":["Doppelte Ablenkung gewinnt entscheidend Material.","Bauer und Turm locken nacheinander die Verteidiger weg, dann schlägt die Dame zu.","Bauer nach h6 – die erste Ablenkung der Gewinnkombination."],"en":["A double deflection wins decisive material.","Pawn and rook lure away defenders one by one, then the queen strikes.","Pawn to h6 — the first deflection of the winning combination."],"hr":["Dvostruko odvlačenje osvaja odlučujući materijal.","Pješak i top redom odvlače branitelje, zatim dama udara.","Pješak na h6 — prvo odvlačenje dobitne kombinacije."]}', HintsVersion=1 WHERE LineId LIKE '%:013.055' AND BookFileName='chessable-u5-21646.pgn';
UPDATE BookPuzzles SET HintsJson='{"de":["Ein erzwungenes Matt steht bereit.","Ein Läuferopfer und die zentralen Figuren weben das Mattnetz.","Dame nimmt auf d5 – beginnt das erzwungene Matt."],"en":["A forced mate is available.","A bishop sacrifice and the central pieces weave the mating net.","Queen takes on d5 — begins the forced mate."],"hr":["Prisilni mat je na raspolaganju.","Žrtva lovca i središnje figure pletu matnu mrežu.","Dama uzima na d5 — započinje prisilni mat."]}', HintsVersion=1 WHERE LineId LIKE '%:013.056' AND BookFileName='chessable-u5-21646.pgn';
UPDATE BookPuzzles SET HintsJson='{"de":["Ein erzwungenes Matt auf der Grundreihe wartet.","Ein Damenopfer lenkt den Verteidiger der Grundreihe ab.","Turm nimmt auf f2 – startet das Grundreihenmatt."],"en":["A forced back-rank mate awaits.","A queen sacrifice lures away the back-rank defender.","Rook takes on f2 — sets up the back-rank mate."],"hr":["Čeka prisilni mat na zadnjem redu.","Žrtva dame odvlači branitelja zadnjeg reda.","Top uzima na f2 — postavlja mat na zadnjem redu."]}', HintsVersion=1 WHERE LineId LIKE '%:013.057' AND BookFileName='chessable-u5-21646.pgn';
UPDATE BookPuzzles SET HintsJson='{"de":["Ein erzwungenes Matt liegt für dich bereit.","Ein Bauernopfer öffnet Linien, dann übernehmen Läufer und Türme.","Bauer nach g5 – beginnt die Mattkombination."],"en":["A forced mate is ready for you.","A pawn sacrifice opens lines, then bishop and rooks take over.","Pawn to g5 — begins the mating combination."],"hr":["Prisilni mat te čeka.","Žrtva pješaka otvara linije, zatim lovac i topovi preuzimaju.","Pješak na g5 — započinje matnu kombinaciju."]}', HintsVersion=1 WHERE LineId LIKE '%:013.058' AND BookFileName='chessable-u5-21646.pgn';
UPDATE BookPuzzles SET HintsJson='{"de":["Ein ruhiger Zug entlarvt eine überlastete Figur und gewinnt eine Figur.","Ein Bauernstoß greift einen Springer an und legt eine Tauschfolge offen.","Bauer nach a3 – beginnt die Kombination, die eine Figur gewinnt."],"en":["A quiet move exposes an overworked piece and wins a piece.","A pawn thrust attacks a knight and reveals a winning exchange sequence.","Pawn to a3 — starts the combination that wins a piece."],"hr":["Tihi potez razotkriva preopterećenu figuru i osvaja figuru.","Prodor pješaka napada skakača i otkriva dobitni niz razmjena.","Pješak na a3 — započinje kombinaciju koja osvaja figuru."]}', HintsVersion=1 WHERE LineId LIKE '%:013.059' AND BookFileName='chessable-u5-21646.pgn';
UPDATE BookPuzzles SET HintsJson='{"de":["Ein erzwungenes Matt wartet auf dich.","Ein Bauernvorstoß öffnet ein Abzugsspiel mit Doppeldrohung.","Bauer nach a2 – startet die Mattkombination."],"en":["A forced mate awaits you.","A pawn advance unleashes a discovered attack with a double threat.","Pawn to a2 — starts the mating combination."],"hr":["Prisilni mat te čeka.","Prodor pješaka pokreće otkriveni napad s dvostrukom prijetnjom.","Pješak na a2 — započinje matnu kombinaciju."]}', HintsVersion=1 WHERE LineId LIKE '%:013.060' AND BookFileName='chessable-u5-21646.pgn';
UPDATE BookPuzzles SET HintsJson='{"de":["Ein erzwungenes Matt steht bereit.","Ein Turmopfer öffnet den König, dann übernehmen Dame und Turm.","Turm nimmt auf g2 – beginnt das erzwungene Matt."],"en":["A forced mate is available.","A rook sacrifice cracks open the king, then queen and rook take over.","Rook takes on g2 — begins the forced mate."],"hr":["Prisilni mat je na raspolaganju.","Žrtva topa razgolićuje kralja, zatim dama i top preuzimaju.","Top uzima na g2 — započinje prisilni mat."]}', HintsVersion=1 WHERE LineId LIKE '%:013.061' AND BookFileName='chessable-u5-21646.pgn';
UPDATE BookPuzzles SET HintsJson='{"de":["Ein erzwungenes Matt liegt in der Luft.","Ein Springerschlag und die Verstellung der langen Diagonale ebnen den Weg.","Springer nimmt auf c6 – beginnt das erzwungene Matt."],"en":["A forced mate is in the air.","A knight capture and interference on the long diagonal pave the way.","Knight takes on c6 — begins the forced mate."],"hr":["Prisilni mat visi u zraku.","Uzimanje skakačem i presijecanje duge dijagonale otvaraju put.","Skakač uzima na c6 — započinje prisilni mat."]}', HintsVersion=1 WHERE LineId LIKE '%:013.062' AND BookFileName='chessable-u5-21646.pgn';
UPDATE BookPuzzles SET HintsJson='{"de":["Ein Ablenkungsopfer bereitet einen Doppelangriff vor, der Material gewinnt.","Erst wird ein Bauer weggelockt, dann gabeln die Springer.","Dame nach h5 – leitet die materialgewinnende Kombination ein."],"en":["A deflection sacrifice prepares a double attack that wins material.","First a pawn is lured away, then the knights fork.","Queen to h5 — initiates the material-winning combination."],"hr":["Žrtva odvlačenja priprema dvostruki napad koji osvaja materijal.","Najprije se odvlači pješak, zatim skakači daju vilicu.","Dama na h5 — pokreće kombinaciju koja osvaja materijal."]}', HintsVersion=1 WHERE LineId LIKE '%:013.063' AND BookFileName='chessable-u5-21646.pgn';
UPDATE BookPuzzles SET HintsJson='{"de":["Ein Spieß gegen die gefesselte Figur gewinnt eine ganze Figur.","Erst ein Bauernvorstoß, dann legt sich der Läufer auf die entscheidende Linie.","Bauer nach b5 – beginnt die Kombination, die einen Springer gewinnt."],"en":["A skewer against the pinned piece wins a whole piece.","First a pawn push, then the bishop lines up on the decisive file.","Pawn to b5 — starts the combination that wins a knight."],"hr":["Nabod na vezanu figuru osvaja cijelu figuru.","Najprije prodor pješaka, zatim se lovac postavlja na odlučujuću liniju.","Pješak na b5 — započinje kombinaciju koja osvaja skakača."]}', HintsVersion=1 WHERE LineId LIKE '%:013.064' AND BookFileName='chessable-u5-21646.pgn';
UPDATE BookPuzzles SET HintsJson='{"de":["Ein Bauerndurchbruch im Zentrum führt zu entscheidendem Materialgewinn.","Der Vorstoß stellt den Springer und enttarnt eine eigene blockierte Figur.","Bauer nach d5 – beginnt die gewinnende Kombination."],"en":["A central pawn break leads to decisive material gain.","The advance attacks the knight that blocks its own bishop.","Pawn to d5 — begins the winning combination."],"hr":["Prodor pješaka u centru vodi do odlučujuće materijalne prednosti.","Prodor napada skakača koji blokira vlastitog lovca.","Pješak na d5 — započinje dobitnu kombinaciju."]}', HintsVersion=1 WHERE LineId LIKE '%:013.065' AND BookFileName='chessable-u5-21646.pgn';
UPDATE BookPuzzles SET HintsJson='{"de":["Eine Ablenkung des Damenverteidigers gewinnt entscheidend Material.","Erst zieht die Dame zur Seite, dann lockt ein Turmopfer den Verteidiger weg.","Dame nach h4 – leitet die gewinnende Kombination ein."],"en":["Deflecting the queen''s defender wins decisive material.","First the queen sidesteps, then a rook sacrifice lures the defender away.","Queen to h4 — initiates the winning combination."],"hr":["Odvlačenje branitelja dame osvaja odlučujući materijal.","Najprije se dama izmiče, zatim žrtva topa odvlači branitelja.","Dama na h4 — pokreće dobitnu kombinaciju."]}', HintsVersion=1 WHERE LineId LIKE '%:013.066' AND BookFileName='chessable-u5-21646.pgn';
UPDATE BookPuzzles SET HintsJson='{"de":["Ein Spieß gewinnt entscheidend Material.","Ein vorrückender Bauer und die Dame fangen die gegnerische Dame.","Bauer nach b6 – beginnt die Kombination, die die Dame spießt."],"en":["A skewer wins decisive material.","An advancing pawn and the queen trap the enemy queen.","Pawn to b6 — starts the combination that skewers the queen."],"hr":["Nabod osvaja odlučujući materijal.","Prodorni pješak i dama hvataju protivničku damu.","Pješak na b6 — započinje kombinaciju koja nabada damu."]}', HintsVersion=1 WHERE LineId LIKE '%:013.067' AND BookFileName='chessable-u5-21646.pgn';
UPDATE BookPuzzles SET HintsJson='{"de":["Ein erzwungenes Matt liegt für dich bereit.","Zwei Schlagopfer reißen die Königsstellung auf, dann setzt die Dame.","Turm nimmt auf h4 – beginnt das erzwungene Matt."],"en":["A forced mate is ready for you.","Two sacrifices rip open the king, then the queen delivers mate.","Rook takes on h4 — begins the forced mate."],"hr":["Prisilni mat te čeka.","Dvije žrtve razgolićuju kralja, zatim dama matira.","Top uzima na h4 — započinje prisilni mat."]}', HintsVersion=1 WHERE LineId LIKE '%:013.068' AND BookFileName='chessable-u5-21646.pgn';
UPDATE BookPuzzles SET HintsJson='{"de":["Ein Königslockungsopfer leitet einen Abzugsangriff ein, der Material gewinnt.","Erst wird der König gelockt, dann nutzt ein Abzug die gefesselte Dame.","Dame nimmt auf f8 – beginnt die materialgewinnende Kombination."],"en":["A king-decoy sacrifice sets up a discovered attack that wins material.","First the king is lured out, then a discovery exploits the pinned queen.","Queen takes on f8 — begins the material-winning combination."],"hr":["Žrtva mamljenja kralja priprema otkriveni napad koji osvaja materijal.","Najprije se kralj namami, zatim otkrivanje iskorištava vezanu damu.","Dama uzima na f8 — započinje kombinaciju koja osvaja materijal."]}', HintsVersion=1 WHERE LineId LIKE '%:013.069' AND BookFileName='chessable-u5-21646.pgn';
UPDATE BookPuzzles SET HintsJson='{"de":["Vorsicht: ein scheinbarer Verstellungszug verliert eine Figur an den Gegner.","Der Läufer betritt ein verwundbares Feld, wo ihn der Springer fängt.","Läufer nach b4 – doch der Springerangriff gewinnt die Figur zurück."],"en":["Beware: a tempting interference move loses a piece to the opponent.","The bishop steps onto a vulnerable square where the knight traps it.","Bishop to b4 — but the knight''s attack wins the piece back."],"hr":["Oprez: primamljiv potez presijecanja gubi figuru protivniku.","Lovac stupa na ranjivo polje gdje ga skakač hvata.","Lovac na b4 — no napad skakača vraća figuru."]}', HintsVersion=1 WHERE LineId LIKE '%:013.070' AND BookFileName='chessable-u5-21646.pgn';
UPDATE BookPuzzles SET HintsJson='{"de":["Ein Ablenkungsopfer ebnet einen Angriff, der entscheidend Material gewinnt.","Erst lockt ein Läuferopfer eine Figur weg, dann öffnen sich Linien zum König.","Läufer nimmt auf a6 – leitet die gewinnende Kombination ein."],"en":["A deflection sacrifice clears the way for a decisive material-winning attack.","First a bishop sacrifice lures a piece away, then lines open to the king.","Bishop takes on a6 — initiates the winning combination."],"hr":["Žrtva odvlačenja otvara put napadu koji osvaja odlučujući materijal.","Najprije žrtva lovca odvlači figuru, zatim se otvaraju linije prema kralju.","Lovac uzima na a6 — pokreće dobitnu kombinaciju."]}', HintsVersion=1 WHERE LineId LIKE '%:013.071' AND BookFileName='chessable-u5-21646.pgn';
UPDATE BookPuzzles SET HintsJson='{"de":["Ein Springerschlag und eine Gabel gewinnen Material.","Der Springer schlägt ins Herz der Stellung und springt dann zur Gabel.","Springer nimmt auf d7 – beginnt die materialgewinnende Folge."],"en":["A knight capture and a fork win material.","The knight strikes into the heart of the position, then leaps to fork.","Knight takes on d7 — begins the material-winning sequence."],"hr":["Uzimanje skakačem i vilica osvajaju materijal.","Skakač udara u srce pozicije, zatim skače na vilicu.","Skakač uzima na d7 — započinje niz koji osvaja materijal."]}', HintsVersion=1 WHERE LineId LIKE '%:013.072' AND BookFileName='chessable-u5-21646.pgn';
UPDATE BookPuzzles SET HintsJson='{"de":["Das Räumen einer Diagonale leitet einen materialgewinnenden Vorstoß ein.","Ein Bauernopfer öffnet die Diagonale, dann marschiert der Bauer durch.","Bauer nach e3 – beginnt die gewinnende Kombination."],"en":["Clearing a diagonal sets up a material-winning advance.","A pawn sacrifice opens the diagonal, then the pawn marches through.","Pawn to e3 — begins the winning combination."],"hr":["Čišćenje dijagonale priprema prodor koji osvaja materijal.","Žrtva pješaka otvara dijagonalu, zatim pješak prodire.","Pješak na e3 — započinje dobitnu kombinaciju."]}', HintsVersion=1 WHERE LineId LIKE '%:013.073' AND BookFileName='chessable-u5-21646.pgn';
UPDATE BookPuzzles SET HintsJson='{"de":["Ein Lockopfer zieht den Läufer auf ein ungünstiges Feld und gewinnt Material.","Erst wird der Läufer geködert, dann brechen Dame und Turm zum König durch.","Bauer nach f4 – leitet die materialgewinnende Kombination ein."],"en":["A luring sacrifice draws the bishop to a bad square and wins material.","First the bishop is baited, then queen and rook break through to the king.","Pawn to f4 — initiates the material-winning combination."],"hr":["Mameća žrtva privlači lovca na loše polje i osvaja materijal.","Najprije se lovac namami, zatim dama i top probijaju prema kralju.","Pješak na f4 — pokreće kombinaciju koja osvaja materijal."]}', HintsVersion=1 WHERE LineId LIKE '%:013.074' AND BookFileName='chessable-u5-21646.pgn';
UPDATE BookPuzzles SET HintsJson='{"de":["Ein Schlagopfer schafft eine Mattdrohung und gewinnt entscheidend Material.","Erst nimmt die Dame eine Figur, dann jagt sie um den König und gewinnt.","Dame nimmt auf f8 – beginnt die gewinnende Kombination."],"en":["A capture creating a mate threat wins decisive material.","First the queen grabs a piece, then she hunts around the king to win.","Queen takes on f8 — begins the winning combination."],"hr":["Uzimanje koje stvara prijetnju mata osvaja odlučujući materijal.","Najprije dama uzima figuru, zatim juri oko kralja i pobjeđuje.","Dama uzima na f8 — započinje dobitnu kombinaciju."]}', HintsVersion=1 WHERE LineId LIKE '%:013.075' AND BookFileName='chessable-u5-21646.pgn';
UPDATE BookPuzzles SET HintsJson='{"de":["Ein erzwungenes Matt wartet auf dich.","Ein Turmopfer lockt den König, dann übernimmt die Dame.","Turm nimmt auf c1 – beginnt das erzwungene Matt."],"en":["A forced mate awaits you.","A rook sacrifice draws the king out, then the queen takes over.","Rook takes on c1 — begins the forced mate."],"hr":["Prisilni mat te čeka.","Žrtva topa izvlači kralja, zatim dama preuzima.","Top uzima na c1 — započinje prisilni mat."]}', HintsVersion=1 WHERE LineId LIKE '%:013.076' AND BookFileName='chessable-u5-21646.pgn';
UPDATE BookPuzzles SET HintsJson='{"de":["Ein Lockopfer zieht den Läufer aufs Brett und gewinnt Material per Gabel.","Erst wird der Läufer geködert, dann gabelt der Springer mehrere Ziele.","Läufer nimmt auf d5 – beginnt die materialgewinnende Kombination."],"en":["A luring sacrifice draws the bishop in and wins material by a fork.","First the bishop is baited, then the knight forks several targets.","Bishop takes on d5 — begins the material-winning combination."],"hr":["Mameća žrtva privlači lovca i osvaja materijal vilicom.","Najprije se lovac namami, zatim skakač vilicom napada više ciljeva.","Lovac uzima na d5 — započinje kombinaciju koja osvaja materijal."]}', HintsVersion=1 WHERE LineId LIKE '%:013.077' AND BookFileName='chessable-u5-21646.pgn';
UPDATE BookPuzzles SET HintsJson='{"de":["Ein Schlagopfer öffnet die lange Diagonale und gewinnt entscheidend Material.","Erst wird der König gejagt, dann schlägt die Dame entlang der Diagonale durch.","Turm nimmt auf f6 – leitet die gewinnende Kombination ein."],"en":["A capture opening the long diagonal wins decisive material.","First the king is chased, then the queen strikes along the diagonal.","Rook takes on f6 — initiates the winning combination."],"hr":["Uzimanje koje otvara dugu dijagonalu osvaja odlučujući materijal.","Najprije se kralj progoni, zatim dama udara duž dijagonale.","Top uzima na f6 — pokreće dobitnu kombinaciju."]}', HintsVersion=1 WHERE LineId LIKE '%:013.078' AND BookFileName='chessable-u5-21646.pgn';
UPDATE BookPuzzles SET HintsJson='{"de":["Ein Bauernvorstoß greift einen Springer an und führt zu entscheidendem Vorteil.","Der Vorstoß stört die Verteidigung, dann dreht die Dame an der Schraube.","Bauer nach e5 – beginnt die gewinnende Kombination."],"en":["A pawn advance attacks a knight and leads to a decisive advantage.","The push disrupts the defence, then the queen turns the screw.","Pawn to e5 — begins the winning combination."],"hr":["Prodor pješaka napada skakača i vodi do odlučujuće prednosti.","Prodor remeti obranu, zatim dama pritišće.","Pješak na e5 — započinje dobitnu kombinaciju."]}', HintsVersion=1 WHERE LineId LIKE '%:013.079' AND BookFileName='chessable-u5-21646.pgn';
UPDATE BookPuzzles SET HintsJson='{"de":["Ein Turm-Manöver entscheidet zugunsten von Weiß.","Der schwere Turm bringt die entscheidende Kraft an den feindlichen König.","Turm nach h8 – beginnt die gewinnende Kombination."],"en":["A rook maneuver wins decisive material here.","The rook swings over to overwhelm the enemy king.","Rook to h8 — starts the winning combination."],"hr":["Manevar topom donosi odlučujuću prednost.","Top se prebacuje da nadjača neprijateljskog kralja.","Top na h8 — započinje dobitnu kombinaciju."]}', HintsVersion=1 WHERE LineId LIKE '%:013.080' AND BookFileName='chessable-u5-21646.pgn';
UPDATE BookPuzzles SET HintsJson='{"de":["Ein Bauerndurchbruch öffnet die Stellung zum Vorteil.","Ein Bauer reißt die Deckung vor dem König auf, dann schlagen die Figuren zu.","Bauer nach g5 – leitet die gewinnende Kombination ein."],"en":["A pawn break tears open the position for a decisive edge.","A pawn rips open the king''s cover so the pieces can strike.","Pawn to g5 — begins the winning combination."],"hr":["Pješački proboj otvara poziciju za odlučujuću prednost.","Pješak razbija zaštitu kralja kako bi figure udarile.","Pješak na g5 — započinje dobitnu kombinaciju."]}', HintsVersion=1 WHERE LineId LIKE '%:013.081' AND BookFileName='chessable-u5-21646.pgn';
UPDATE BookPuzzles SET HintsJson='{"de":["Ein Schlagopfer lockt eine Figur weg und gewinnt Material.","Erst stört man die Verteidigung, dann folgt ein Abzug mit dem Springer.","Turm schlägt auf e1 – Auftakt der gewinnenden Kombination."],"en":["A capture sacrifice lures a defender away and wins material.","Disrupt the defense first, then a knight discovery decides.","Rook takes on e1 — the start of the winning combination."],"hr":["Žrtva uzimanjem odvlači branitelja i osvaja materijal.","Prvo se remeti obrana, zatim slijedi otkriveni napad skakačem.","Top uzima na e1 — početak dobitne kombinacije."]}', HintsVersion=1 WHERE LineId LIKE '%:013.082' AND BookFileName='chessable-u5-21646.pgn';
UPDATE BookPuzzles SET HintsJson='{"de":["Mit präzisen Damenzügen gewinnt Weiß entscheidend Material.","Die Dame manövriert, um den Läufer mit einer Gabel zu erwischen.","Dame nach h7 – Beginn der gewinnenden Kombination."],"en":["Precise queen moves win decisive material.","The queen maneuvers to fork and snare a piece.","Queen to h7 — the start of the winning combination."],"hr":["Preciznim potezima damom bijeli osvaja odlučujući materijal.","Dama manevrira da viljuškom uhvati figuru.","Dama na h7 — početak dobitne kombinacije."]}', HintsVersion=1 WHERE LineId LIKE '%:013.083' AND BookFileName='chessable-u5-21646.pgn';
UPDATE BookPuzzles SET HintsJson='{"de":["Ein Schlagopfer öffnet die Bahn zu einem gewinnenden Angriff.","Erst opfert der Läufer, dann dringt eine schwere Figur entscheidend ein.","Läufer schlägt auf g4 – Auftakt der gewinnenden Kombination."],"en":["A sacrifice clears the way for a decisive attack.","The bishop sacrifices so a heavy piece can crash through.","Bishop takes on g4 — the start of the winning combination."],"hr":["Žrtva otvara put odlučujućem napadu.","Lovac se žrtvuje da teška figura prodre.","Lovac uzima na g4 — početak dobitne kombinacije."]}', HintsVersion=1 WHERE LineId LIKE '%:013.084' AND BookFileName='chessable-u5-21646.pgn';
