UPDATE BookPuzzles SET HintsJson='{"de":["Schwarz hat ein erzwungenes Matt.","Die Dame treibt den König Schritt für Schritt in die Ecke.","Dame nach e2 – Beginn der erzwungenen Mattführung."],"en":["Black has a forced mate.","The queen herds the king step by step into the corner.","Queen to e2 — the forced mate begins."],"hr":["Crni ima prisilni mat.","Dama korak po korak tjera kralja u kut.","Dama na e2 — počinje prisilni mat."]}', HintsVersion=1 WHERE LineId LIKE '%:004.036' AND BookFileName='chessable-u5-49693.pgn';
UPDATE BookPuzzles SET HintsJson='{"de":["Eine Kombination verschafft Weiß einen entscheidenden Vorteil.","Ein Turmopfer lockt den König, dann fängt das Läuferpaar ihn endgültig ein.","Turm nimmt auf h7 – Auftakt zur entscheidenden Kombination."],"en":["A combination gives White a decisive advantage.","A rook sacrifice lures the king, then the bishop pair finishes the job.","Rook takes on h7 — the start of the decisive combination."],"hr":["Kombinacija daje bijelom odlučujuću prednost.","Žrtva topa mami kralja, a tada par lovaca dovršava posao.","Top uzima na h7 — početak odlučujuće kombinacije."]}', HintsVersion=1 WHERE LineId LIKE '%:004.037' AND BookFileName='chessable-u5-49693.pgn';
UPDATE BookPuzzles SET HintsJson='{"de":["Weiß erzwingt in wenigen Zügen das Matt.","Ein Turmopfer auf der offenen Linie lockt den Verteidiger weg, dann entscheidet die Dame.","Turm nach e8 – Auftakt zum erzwungenen Matt."],"en":["White forces mate in a few moves.","A rook sacrifice on the open file deflects the defender, then the queen decides.","Rook to e8 — the start of the forced mate."],"hr":["Bijeli prisiljava mat u nekoliko poteza.","Žrtva topa na otvorenoj liniji odvlači branitelja, a tada dama odlučuje.","Top na e8 — početak prisilnog mata."]}', HintsVersion=1 WHERE LineId LIKE '%:004.038' AND BookFileName='chessable-u5-49693.pgn';
