UPDATE BookPuzzles SET HintsJson='{"de":["Schwarz hat ein erzwungenes Matt über mehrere Züge.","Die Dame nähert sich im Treppenschritt unaufhaltsam dem weißen König.","Dame nach c6 – Beginn der erzwungenen Treppen-Mattführung."],"en":["Black has a forced mate spanning several moves.","The queen climbs toward the white king with an unstoppable staircase march.","Queen to c6 — the start of the forced staircase mate."],"hr":["Crni ima prisilni mat kroz nekoliko poteza.","Dama se stepenastim hodom nezaustavljivo približava bijelom kralju.","Dama na c6 — početak prisilnog stepenastog mata."]}', HintsVersion=1 WHERE LineId LIKE '%:004.055' AND BookFileName='chessable-u5-49693.pgn';
UPDATE BookPuzzles SET HintsJson='{"de":["Hier steckt ein erzwungenes Matt – treib den König ins Freie.","Die schweren Figuren bündeln ihre Kraft gegen den schwachen Königsflügel.","Dame schlägt auf h7 – Auftakt zum erzwungenen Matt."],"en":["A forced mate is here — drag the king into the open.","The heavy pieces combine their force against the weak kingside.","Queen takes on h7 — the start of a forced mate."],"hr":["Tu postoji prisilni mat — izvuci kralja na otvoreno.","Teške figure udružuju snagu protiv slabog kraljevog krila.","Dama uzima na h7 — početak prisilnog mata."]}', HintsVersion=1 WHERE LineId LIKE '%:004.056' AND BookFileName='chessable-u5-49693.pgn';
UPDATE BookPuzzles SET HintsJson='{"de":["Ein erzwungenes Matt liegt in der Luft – schnüre den König ein.","Springer und Läufer arbeiten zusammen, um das Netz zuzuziehen.","Springer nach g4 – Beginn der erzwungenen Mattführung."],"en":["A forced mate is in the air — fence the king in.","Knight and bishop work together to draw the net tight.","Knight to g4 — the start of the forced mating sequence."],"hr":["Prisilni mat je u zraku — zatvori kralja u mrežu.","Skakač i lovac surađuju da stegnu mrežu.","Skakač na g4 — početak prisilnog matnog niza."]}', HintsVersion=1 WHERE LineId LIKE '%:004.057' AND BookFileName='chessable-u5-49693.pgn';
UPDATE BookPuzzles SET HintsJson='{"de":["Du kannst ein Matt erzwingen – das Opfer reißt die Königsstellung auf.","Der Turm bahnt sich den Weg, die Dame setzt den Schlusspunkt.","Turm schlägt auf b2 – Auftakt zum erzwungenen Matt."],"en":["You can force mate — the sacrifice tears open the king''s shelter.","The rook blasts the way open and the queen delivers the finish.","Rook takes on b2 — the start of a forced mate."],"hr":["Možeš prisiliti mat — žrtva razbija kraljev zaklon.","Top probija put, a dama zadaje završni udarac.","Top uzima na b2 — početak prisilnog mata."]}', HintsVersion=1 WHERE LineId LIKE '%:004.058' AND BookFileName='chessable-u5-49693.pgn';
UPDATE BookPuzzles SET HintsJson='{"de":["Eine Kombination erzwingt eine entscheidende Doppeldrohung.","Turm und Springer drohen gemeinsam, der König kann nicht beidem ausweichen.","Turm nach b5 – die unparierbare Doppeldrohung entscheidet."],"en":["A combination sets up a decisive double threat.","Rook and knight threaten together and the king cannot meet both.","Rook to b5 — the unstoppable double threat decides."],"hr":["Kombinacija stvara odlučujuću dvostruku prijetnju.","Top i skakač prijete zajedno, a kralj ne može obraniti oba.","Top na b5 — neobranjiva dvostruka prijetnja odlučuje."]}', HintsVersion=1 WHERE LineId LIKE '%:004.059' AND BookFileName='chessable-u5-49693.pgn';
UPDATE BookPuzzles SET HintsJson='{"de":["Ein Manöver gewinnt entscheidend, indem es eine Mattdrohung aufbaut.","Der Springer springt weg und gibt dem Turm den entscheidenden Weg frei.","Springer nach f8 – leitet die gewinnbringende Mattdrohung ein."],"en":["A maneuver wins decisively by setting up a mating threat.","The knight steps away to clear the decisive path for the rook.","Knight to f8 — launches the winning mating threat."],"hr":["Manevar odlučujuće pobjeđuje stvarajući prijetnju matom.","Skakač se uklanja i otvara odlučujući put topu.","Skakač na f8 — pokreće pobjedonosnu prijetnju matom."]}', HintsVersion=1 WHERE LineId LIKE '%:004.060' AND BookFileName='chessable-u5-49693.pgn';
UPDATE BookPuzzles SET HintsJson='{"de":["Hier gibt es ein erzwungenes Matt – locke den König ins Verderben.","Ein Opfer zieht den König heran, dann schlägt der zweite Turm zu.","Turm schlägt auf f8 – Beginn der erzwungenen Mattführung."],"en":["There is a forced mate here — lure the king to its doom.","A sacrifice drags the king out, then the second rook strikes.","Rook takes on f8 — the start of the forced mating sequence."],"hr":["Tu postoji prisilni mat — namami kralja u propast.","Žrtva privlači kralja, a zatim udara drugi top.","Top uzima na f8 — početak prisilnog matnog niza."]}', HintsVersion=1 WHERE LineId LIKE '%:004.061' AND BookFileName='chessable-u5-49693.pgn';
UPDATE BookPuzzles SET HintsJson='{"de":["Ein erzwungenes Matt steht bereit – das Ablenkungsopfer ist der Schlüssel.","Der Turm opfert sich, damit die Dame entscheidend eindringt.","Turm nach d8 – Auftakt zum erzwungenen Matt."],"en":["A forced mate is ready — the decoy sacrifice is the key.","The rook sacrifices itself so the queen can break in decisively.","Rook to d8 — the start of a forced mate."],"hr":["Prisilni mat je spreman — žrtva-mamac je ključ.","Top se žrtvuje da dama odlučujuće prodre.","Top na d8 — početak prisilnog mata."]}', HintsVersion=1 WHERE LineId LIKE '%:004.062' AND BookFileName='chessable-u5-49693.pgn';
UPDATE BookPuzzles SET HintsJson='{"de":["Ein erzwungenes Matt wartet – der Turm dringt unaufhaltsam ein.","Turm und Springer treiben den König in ein tödliches Netz.","Turm schlägt auf f6 – Beginn der erzwungenen Mattführung."],"en":["A forced mate awaits — the rook penetrates unstoppably.","Rook and knight herd the king into a deadly net.","Rook takes on f6 — the start of the forced mating sequence."],"hr":["Prisilni mat čeka — top nezaustavljivo prodire.","Top i skakač tjeraju kralja u smrtonosnu mrežu.","Top uzima na f6 — početak prisilnog matnog niza."]}', HintsVersion=1 WHERE LineId LIKE '%:004.063' AND BookFileName='chessable-u5-49693.pgn';
UPDATE BookPuzzles SET HintsJson='{"de":["Du kannst ein Matt erzwingen – der König wird ins Eck gedrängt.","Der Turm beherrscht die entscheidende Linie, die Bauern stützen den Angriff.","Turm nach a1 – Auftakt zur erzwungenen Mattführung."],"en":["You can force mate — the king is driven into the corner.","The rook rules the key file while the pawns support the attack.","Rook to a1 — the start of the forced mating sequence."],"hr":["Možeš prisiliti mat — kralj je natjeran u kut.","Top vlada ključnom linijom dok pješaci podupiru napad.","Top na a1 — početak prisilnog matnog niza."]}', HintsVersion=1 WHERE LineId LIKE '%:004.064' AND BookFileName='chessable-u5-49693.pgn';
UPDATE BookPuzzles SET HintsJson='{"de":["Ein erzwungenes Matt liegt vor – treib den König mit Dame und Springer.","Die Dame jagt den König, während der Springer das Netz festhält.","Bauer nach e5 – Auftakt zur langen erzwungenen Mattführung."],"en":["A forced mate is here — drive the king with queen and knight.","The queen hunts the king while the knight holds the net.","Pawn to e5 — the start of the long forced mating sequence."],"hr":["Prisilni mat je pred tobom — tjeraj kralja damom i skakačem.","Dama lovi kralja dok skakač drži mrežu.","Pješak na e5 — početak dugog prisilnog matnog niza."]}', HintsVersion=1 WHERE LineId LIKE '%:004.065' AND BookFileName='chessable-u5-49693.pgn';
UPDATE BookPuzzles SET HintsJson='{"de":["Hier ist ein erzwungenes Matt – das Opfer öffnet den König.","Dame und Läufer arbeiten am entblößten König zusammen.","Turm schlägt auf h3 – Auftakt zum erzwungenen Matt."],"en":["A forced mate is here — the sacrifice opens up the king.","Queen and bishop combine against the exposed king.","Rook takes on h3 — the start of a forced mate."],"hr":["Tu je prisilni mat — žrtva otvara kralja.","Dama i lovac surađuju protiv izloženog kralja.","Top uzima na h3 — početak prisilnog mata."]}', HintsVersion=1 WHERE LineId LIKE '%:004.066' AND BookFileName='chessable-u5-49693.pgn';
UPDATE BookPuzzles SET HintsJson='{"de":["Ein erzwungenes Matt wartet – räume die Verteidiger mit Opfern weg.","Türme und Dame dringen über die offenen Linien zum König durch.","Turm schlägt auf e1 – Auftakt zum erzwungenen Matt."],"en":["A forced mate awaits — clear the defenders with sacrifices.","Rooks and queen break through the open lines to the king.","Rook takes on e1 — the start of a forced mate."],"hr":["Prisilni mat čeka — žrtvama ukloni branitelje.","Topovi i dama probijaju do kralja po otvorenim linijama.","Top uzima na e1 — početak prisilnog mata."]}', HintsVersion=1 WHERE LineId LIKE '%:004.067' AND BookFileName='chessable-u5-49693.pgn';
UPDATE BookPuzzles SET HintsJson='{"de":["Du kannst Matt erzwingen – treib den König in ein enges Netz.","Dame, Läufer und Bauern jagen den blanken König gemeinsam.","Dame nach f8 – Auftakt zur erzwungenen Mattführung."],"en":["You can force mate — drive the king into a tight net.","Queen, bishop and pawns hunt the bare king together.","Queen to f8 — the start of the forced mating sequence."],"hr":["Možeš prisiliti mat — tjeraj kralja u tijesnu mrežu.","Dama, lovac i pješaci zajedno love golog kralja.","Dama na f8 — početak prisilnog matnog niza."]}', HintsVersion=1 WHERE LineId LIKE '%:004.068' AND BookFileName='chessable-u5-49693.pgn';
UPDATE BookPuzzles SET HintsJson='{"de":["Der Angriff lässt sich mit Matt abschließen – locke den König heraus.","Opfere, um die Verteidiger zu beseitigen, dann setzt die Dame Matt.","Springer schlägt auf c6 – Auftakt zum erzwungenen Matt."],"en":["The attack can be finished with mate — lure the king out.","Sacrifice to strip the defenders, then the queen mates.","Knight takes on c6 — the start of a forced mate."],"hr":["Napad se može završiti matom — namami kralja van.","Žrtvuj da ukloniš branitelje, zatim dama matira.","Skakač uzima na c6 — početak prisilnog mata."]}', HintsVersion=1 WHERE LineId LIKE '%:005.003' AND BookFileName='chessable-u5-49693.pgn';
UPDATE BookPuzzles SET HintsJson='{"de":["Lass dich nicht ablenken – hier liegt ein erzwungenes Matt verborgen.","Die Läufer und der Turm jagen den entblößten König über das ganze Brett.","Läufer schlägt auf f3 – Auftakt zur langen erzwungenen Mattführung."],"en":["Don''t be distracted — a forced mate is hidden here.","The bishops and rook hunt the bared king across the board.","Bishop takes on f3 — the start of the long forced mating sequence."],"hr":["Ne daj se odvratiti — tu se krije prisilni mat.","Lovci i top progone ogoljenog kralja po cijeloj ploči.","Lovac uzima na f3 — početak dugog prisilnog matnog niza."]}', HintsVersion=1 WHERE LineId LIKE '%:005.004' AND BookFileName='chessable-u5-49693.pgn';
UPDATE BookPuzzles SET HintsJson='{"de":["Die schwache Grundreihe des Gegners gewinnt entscheidend Material.","Deine Dame nutzt die ungedeckte hinterste Reihe aus.","Dame schlägt auf f6 – gewinnt dank des Grundreihenschwächens."],"en":["The opponent''s weak back rank wins material decisively.","Your queen exploits the undefended last rank.","Queen takes on f6 — winning thanks to the back-rank weakness."],"hr":["Slaba protivnička zadnja linija odlučujuće osvaja materijal.","Tvoja dama iskorištava nebranjenu zadnju liniju.","Dama uzima na f6 — pobjeđuje zbog slabosti zadnje linije."]}', HintsVersion=1 WHERE LineId LIKE '%:005.005' AND BookFileName='chessable-u5-49693.pgn';
UPDATE BookPuzzles SET HintsJson='{"de":["Eine Kombination gewinnt durch die schwache Grundreihe Material.","Die Dame lenkt ab, dann gabelt der Springer entscheidend.","Dame nach b1 – Auftakt zur materialgewinnenden Kombination."],"en":["A combination wins material via the weak back rank.","The queen deflects, then the knight forks decisively.","Queen to b1 — the start of the material-winning combination."],"hr":["Kombinacija osvaja materijal preko slabe zadnje linije.","Dama odvlači, zatim skakač odlučujuće daje viljušku.","Dama na b1 — početak kombinacije koja osvaja materijal."]}', HintsVersion=1 WHERE LineId LIKE '%:005.006' AND BookFileName='chessable-u5-49693.pgn';
UPDATE BookPuzzles SET HintsJson='{"de":["Eine Kombination gewinnt klar Material.","Der zentrale Springer und der starke Läufer wirken zusammen.","Bauer nach c6 – leitet den entscheidenden Materialgewinn ein."],"en":["A combination wins material clearly.","The central knight and the strong bishop work together.","Pawn to c6 — initiates the decisive material gain."],"hr":["Kombinacija jasno osvaja materijal.","Središnji skakač i jaki lovac djeluju zajedno.","Pješak na c6 — pokreće odlučujući dobitak materijala."]}', HintsVersion=1 WHERE LineId LIKE '%:005.007' AND BookFileName='chessable-u5-49693.pgn';
UPDATE BookPuzzles SET HintsJson='{"de":["Der Druck auf der offenen Linie ist entscheidend und gewinnt die Dame.","König und schwere Figuren des Gegners stehen offen – nutze die Linie.","Turm rochiert kurz – baut den entscheidenden Liniendruck auf."],"en":["The pressure down the open file is decisive and wins the queen.","The opponent''s king and heavy pieces sit exposed — use the file.","Rook castles short — building the decisive pressure on the file."],"hr":["Pritisak po otvorenoj liniji je odlučujuć i osvaja damu.","Protivnikov kralj i teške figure su izloženi — iskoristi liniju.","Kratka rokada — gradi odlučujući pritisak po liniji."]}', HintsVersion=1 WHERE LineId LIKE '%:005.008' AND BookFileName='chessable-u5-49693.pgn';
UPDATE BookPuzzles SET HintsJson='{"de":["Ein erzwungenes Matt steht bereit – beseitige zuerst den Verteidiger.","Das Bauernopfer öffnet die Linie für den entscheidenden Turm.","Bauer nach e5 – Auftakt zum erzwungenen Matt."],"en":["A forced mate is ready — remove the defender first.","The pawn sacrifice opens the file for the decisive rook.","Pawn to e5 — the start of a forced mate."],"hr":["Prisilni mat je spreman — prvo ukloni branitelja.","Žrtva pješaka otvara liniju za odlučujući top.","Pješak na e5 — početak prisilnog mata."]}', HintsVersion=1 WHERE LineId LIKE '%:005.009' AND BookFileName='chessable-u5-49693.pgn';
UPDATE BookPuzzles SET HintsJson='{"de":["Eine versteckte Wendung gewinnt eine ganze Figur.","Der Läufer wechselt das Feld und entlarvt eine entscheidende Doppelwirkung.","Läufer nach h5 – gewinnt eine Figur."],"en":["A hidden turn wins a whole piece.","The bishop shifts squares and unveils a decisive double effect.","Bishop to h5 — wins a piece."],"hr":["Skriveni potez osvaja cijelu figuru.","Lovac mijenja polje i otkriva odlučujuće dvostruko djelovanje.","Lovac na h5 — osvaja figuru."]}', HintsVersion=1 WHERE LineId LIKE '%:005.010' AND BookFileName='chessable-u5-49693.pgn';
UPDATE BookPuzzles SET HintsJson='{"de":["Eine Kombination gewinnt klar Material.","Das Turmopfer lockt eine Figur weg, dann schlägt ein Bauer entscheidend zu.","Turm schlägt auf e4 – Auftakt zur materialgewinnenden Kombination."],"en":["A combination wins material clearly.","The rook sacrifice lures a piece away, then a pawn strikes decisively.","Rook takes on e4 — the start of the material-winning combination."],"hr":["Kombinacija jasno osvaja materijal.","Žrtva topa odvlači figuru, zatim pješak odlučujuće udara.","Top uzima na e4 — početak kombinacije koja osvaja materijal."]}', HintsVersion=1 WHERE LineId LIKE '%:005.011' AND BookFileName='chessable-u5-49693.pgn';
UPDATE BookPuzzles SET HintsJson='{"de":["Eine Fesselung gewinnt entscheidend Material.","Der Turm stellt sich so, dass eine Figur ans Kreuz genagelt wird.","Turm nach e6 – diese Selbstfesselung gewinnt Material."],"en":["A pin wins material decisively.","The rook places itself so that a piece gets nailed down.","Rook to e6 — this self-pin wins material."],"hr":["Vezivanje odlučujuće osvaja materijal.","Top se postavlja tako da figura bude prikovana.","Top na e6 — ovo samovezivanje osvaja materijal."]}', HintsVersion=1 WHERE LineId LIKE '%:005.012' AND BookFileName='chessable-u5-49693.pgn';
UPDATE BookPuzzles SET HintsJson='{"de":["Die vorgeprellte gegnerische Dame lässt sich entscheidend fangen.","Türme und Springer kreisen die weit vorgerückte Dame ein.","Turm nach b1 – leitet den Damenfang ein."],"en":["The opponent''s advanced queen can be caught decisively.","Rooks and knight close in on the far-advanced queen.","Rook to b1 — begins the hunt that traps the queen."],"hr":["Protivnička izbačena dama može se odlučujuće uloviti.","Topovi i skakač opkoljavaju daleko izbačenu damu.","Top na b1 — započinje hajku koja lovi damu."]}', HintsVersion=1 WHERE LineId LIKE '%:005.013' AND BookFileName='chessable-u5-49693.pgn';
UPDATE BookPuzzles SET HintsJson='{"de":["Ein ruhiger Zug bereitet eine entscheidende Mattdrohung vor.","Der König weicht aus, damit der Turm mit Schach entscheidend eindringen kann.","König nach g2 – bereitet die gewinnende Mattdrohung vor."],"en":["A quiet move prepares a decisive mating threat.","The king sidesteps so the rook can break in with check decisively.","King to g2 — prepares the winning mating threat."],"hr":["Tihi potez priprema odlučujuću prijetnju matom.","Kralj se uklanja da top odlučujuće prodre sa šahom.","Kralj na g2 — priprema pobjedonosnu prijetnju matom."]}', HintsVersion=1 WHERE LineId LIKE '%:005.014' AND BookFileName='chessable-u5-49693.pgn';
UPDATE BookPuzzles SET HintsJson='{"de":["Eine zerschmetternde Kombination gewinnt entscheidend.","Das Springeropfer reißt den Bauernschild auf, dann brechen die schweren Figuren durch.","Springer schlägt auf e6 – Auftakt zur entscheidenden Kombination."],"en":["A crushing combination wins decisively.","The knight sacrifice tears open the pawn shield, then the heavy pieces break through.","Knight takes on e6 — the start of the decisive combination."],"hr":["Razorna kombinacija odlučujuće pobjeđuje.","Žrtva skakača razbija pješački štit, zatim teške figure probijaju.","Skakač uzima na e6 — početak odlučujuće kombinacije."]}', HintsVersion=1 WHERE LineId LIKE '%:005.015' AND BookFileName='chessable-u5-49693.pgn';
UPDATE BookPuzzles SET HintsJson='{"de":["Die Familiengabel funktioniert und gewinnt entscheidend Material.","Der Springer springt mitten hinein und greift gleich mehrere Ziele an.","Springer nach d3 – diese Gabel leitet den Materialgewinn ein."],"en":["The family fork works and wins material decisively.","The knight leaps into the middle and hits several targets at once.","Knight to d3 — this fork begins the material gain."],"hr":["Obiteljska viljuška djeluje i odlučujuće osvaja materijal.","Skakač uskače u sredinu i napada više meta odjednom.","Skakač na d3 — ova viljuška započinje dobitak materijala."]}', HintsVersion=1 WHERE LineId LIKE '%:005.016' AND BookFileName='chessable-u5-49693.pgn';
UPDATE BookPuzzles SET HintsJson='{"de":["Eine Kombination gewinnt Material, weil das Matt droht.","Der Läufer schlägt ein, dann nutzt die Dame die schwache Königsstellung.","Läufer schlägt auf d4 – Auftakt zur materialgewinnenden Kombination."],"en":["A combination wins material because mate looms.","The bishop strikes, then the queen exploits the weak king position.","Bishop takes on d4 — the start of the material-winning combination."],"hr":["Kombinacija osvaja materijal jer prijeti mat.","Lovac udara, zatim dama iskorištava slab kraljev položaj.","Lovac uzima na d4 — početak kombinacije koja osvaja materijal."]}', HintsVersion=1 WHERE LineId LIKE '%:005.017' AND BookFileName='chessable-u5-49693.pgn';
