UPDATE BookPuzzles SET HintsJson='{"de":["Die nüchterne Fortsetzung sichert den Vorteil.","Der Springer schlägt zu und vereinfacht in eine bessere Stellung.","Springer schlägt auf g6 – die solide vorteilhafte Wahl."],"en":["The sober continuation secures the advantage.","The knight captures and simplifies into a better position.","Knight takes on g6 — the solid, advantageous choice."],"hr":["Trezveni nastavak osigurava prednost.","Skakač uzima i pojednostavljuje u bolju poziciju.","Skakač uzima na g6 — čvrst, povoljan izbor."]}', HintsVersion=1 WHERE LineId LIKE '%:005.028' AND BookFileName='chessable-u5-49693.pgn';
