UPDATE BookPuzzles SET HintsJson='{"de":["Ein Bauerndurchbruch verschafft ein gewonnenes Endspiel.","Der zentrale Turm und ein vorrückender Bauer brechen durch.","Turm schlägt auf d4 – leitet das gewinnende Endspiel ein."],"en":["A pawn breakthrough secures a winning endgame.","The central rook and an advancing pawn force the break.","Rook takes on d4 — leading to the winning endgame."],"hr":["Pješački proboj osigurava dobivenu završnicu.","Središnji top i pješak u napredovanju probijaju.","Top uzima na d4 — vodi u dobivenu završnicu."]}', HintsVersion=1 WHERE LineId LIKE '%:012.072' AND BookFileName='chessable-u5-49693.pgn';
UPDATE BookPuzzles SET HintsJson='{"de":["Eine Opferserie gewinnt entscheidend Material.","Springer und Türme räumen den Weg, dann holt die Dame ab.","Springer schlägt auf e6 – beginnt die gewinnende Kombination."],"en":["A string of sacrifices wins material decisively.","Knight and rook clear the way, then the queen collects.","Knight takes on e6 — starting the winning combination."],"hr":["Niz žrtava osvaja materijal odlučno.","Skakač i topovi raščišćavaju put, a onda dama pokupi.","Skakač uzima na e6 — započinje dobitnu kombinaciju."]}', HintsVersion=1 WHERE LineId LIKE '%:012.073' AND BookFileName='chessable-u5-49693.pgn';
UPDATE BookPuzzles SET HintsJson='{"de":["Weiß ist im Vorteil, doch Schwarz rettet das Remis.","Der vorgeschobene Bauer und der König bilden eine haltbare Festung.","Läufer schlägt auf a5 – beginnt die rettende Folge zum Patt."],"en":["White is up material, but Black saves the draw.","An advancing pawn and the king set up a holdable fortress.","Bishop takes on a5 — starting the saving line to stalemate."],"hr":["Bijeli je u prednosti, ali crni spašava remi.","Napredujući pješak i kralj grade održivu utvrdu.","Lovac uzima na a5 — započinje spasonosni niz do pata."]}', HintsVersion=1 WHERE LineId LIKE '%:012.074' AND BookFileName='chessable-u5-49693.pgn';
UPDATE BookPuzzles SET HintsJson='{"de":["Schwarz hat eine Wendung, die entscheidend Material gewinnt.","Dame und Springer brechen in die weiße Königsstellung ein.","Dame schlägt auf e1 – beginnt die gewinnende Kombination."],"en":["Black has a blow that wins material decisively.","Queen and knight break into the white king''s quarters.","Queen takes on e1 — starting the winning combination."],"hr":["Crni ima udarac koji osvaja materijal odlučno.","Dama i skakač provaljuju u kraljevu poziciju bijelog.","Dama uzima na e1 — započinje dobitnu kombinaciju."]}', HintsVersion=1 WHERE LineId LIKE '%:012.075' AND BookFileName='chessable-u5-49693.pgn';
UPDATE BookPuzzles SET HintsJson='{"de":["Ein ruhiger Zug bereitet einen gewinnenden Angriff vor.","Türme und Dame bündeln sich gegen den schwarzen König.","Turm nach g3 – leitet die gewinnende Kombination ein."],"en":["A quiet move prepares a winning attack.","The rooks and queen gang up on the black king.","Rook to g3 — opening the winning combination."],"hr":["Tihi potez priprema dobitni napad.","Topovi i dama udružuju se protiv crnog kralja.","Top na g3 — pokreće dobitnu kombinaciju."]}', HintsVersion=1 WHERE LineId LIKE '%:012.076' AND BookFileName='chessable-u5-49693.pgn';
UPDATE BookPuzzles SET HintsJson='{"de":["Schwarz hat eine entscheidende Opferwendung.","Die Dame opfert sich, dann gewinnen Springer und Turm.","Dame schlägt auf e1 – beginnt die gewinnende Kombination."],"en":["Black has a decisive sacrificial blow.","The queen sacrifices, then knight and rook do the rest.","Queen takes on e1 — starting the winning combination."],"hr":["Crni ima odlučujući udarac sa žrtvom.","Dama se žrtvuje, a onda dobivaju skakač i top.","Dama uzima na e1 — započinje dobitnu kombinaciju."]}', HintsVersion=1 WHERE LineId LIKE '%:012.077' AND BookFileName='chessable-u5-49693.pgn';
UPDATE BookPuzzles SET HintsJson='{"de":["Ein ruhiger Zug sichert einen entscheidenden Vorteil.","Dame und Turm halten den Druck auf den Königsflügel.","Turm nach g3 – leitet die gewinnende Kombination ein."],"en":["A quiet move secures a decisive advantage.","Queen and rook keep the pressure on the kingside.","Rook to g3 — opening the winning combination."],"hr":["Tihi potez osigurava odlučujuću prednost.","Dama i top održavaju pritisak na kraljevu krilu.","Top na g3 — pokreće dobitnu kombinaciju."]}', HintsVersion=1 WHERE LineId LIKE '%:012.078' AND BookFileName='chessable-u5-49693.pgn';
UPDATE BookPuzzles SET HintsJson='{"de":["Schwarz hat eine Opferkombination, die ein Stück gewinnt.","Die Dame und der doppelte Turm wirken auf der ersten Reihe.","Dame schlägt auf b2 – beginnt die gewinnende Kombination."],"en":["Black has a combination that wins a piece.","The queen and the doubled rook work on the back rank.","Queen takes on b2 — starting the winning combination."],"hr":["Crni ima kombinaciju koja osvaja figuru.","Dama i udvostručeni top djeluju na zadnjoj liniji.","Dama uzima na b2 — započinje dobitnu kombinaciju."]}', HintsVersion=1 WHERE LineId LIKE '%:012.079' AND BookFileName='chessable-u5-49693.pgn';
UPDATE BookPuzzles SET HintsJson='{"de":["Eine Springerwendung sprengt das Zentrum und gewinnt.","Springer und Läufer auf den großen Diagonalen entscheiden.","Springer schlägt auf d6 – beginnt die gewinnende Kombination."],"en":["A knight stroke blows up the center and wins.","Knight and bishop on the long diagonals do the damage.","Knight takes on d6 — starting the winning combination."],"hr":["Potez skakača razbija centar i dobiva.","Skakač i lovac na velikim dijagonalama odlučuju.","Skakač uzima na d6 — započinje dobitnu kombinaciju."]}', HintsVersion=1 WHERE LineId LIKE '%:012.080' AND BookFileName='chessable-u5-49693.pgn';
UPDATE BookPuzzles SET HintsJson='{"de":["Ein zentrales Springeropfer gewinnt entscheidend Material.","Springer und Dame öffnen den Weg zum schwarzen König.","Springer schlägt auf e6 – beginnt die gewinnende Kombination."],"en":["A central knight sacrifice wins material decisively.","Knight and queen pry open the path to the black king.","Knight takes on e6 — starting the winning combination."],"hr":["Žrtva skakača u centru osvaja materijal odlučno.","Skakač i dama otvaraju put prema crnom kralju.","Skakač uzima na e6 — započinje dobitnu kombinaciju."]}', HintsVersion=1 WHERE LineId LIKE '%:012.081' AND BookFileName='chessable-u5-49693.pgn';
UPDATE BookPuzzles SET HintsJson='{"de":["Ein Damenopfer leitet eine gewinnende Wendung ein.","Die Dame opfert sich, dann gewinnt das Zusammenspiel der Figuren.","Dame schlägt auf f6 – beginnt die gewinnende Kombination."],"en":["A queen sacrifice sets up a winning blow.","The queen offers itself, then the pieces coordinate to win.","Queen takes on f6 — starting the winning combination."],"hr":["Žrtva dame pokreće dobitni udarac.","Dama se žrtvuje, a onda figure suradnjom dobivaju.","Dama uzima na f6 — započinje dobitnu kombinaciju."]}', HintsVersion=1 WHERE LineId LIKE '%:012.082' AND BookFileName='chessable-u5-49693.pgn';
UPDATE BookPuzzles SET HintsJson='{"de":["Ein Springeropfer reißt die schwarze Stellung auf und gewinnt.","Springer, Dame und Läufer dringen gemeinsam zum König vor.","Springer schlägt auf e6 – beginnt die gewinnende Kombination."],"en":["A knight sacrifice rips open Black''s position and wins.","Knight, queen and bishop press in toward the king together.","Knight takes on e6 — starting the winning combination."],"hr":["Žrtva skakača razbija crnu poziciju i dobiva.","Skakač, dama i lovac zajedno prodiru prema kralju.","Skakač uzima na e6 — započinje dobitnu kombinaciju."]}', HintsVersion=1 WHERE LineId LIKE '%:012.083' AND BookFileName='chessable-u5-49693.pgn';
UPDATE BookPuzzles SET HintsJson='{"de":["Ein Damenopfer führt zu einer gewinnenden Kombination.","Die Dame und der Läufer auf der langen Diagonale entscheiden.","Dame schlägt auf f6 – beginnt die gewinnende Kombination."],"en":["A queen sacrifice leads to a winning combination.","The queen and the bishop on the long diagonal decide it.","Queen takes on f6 — starting the winning combination."],"hr":["Žrtva dame vodi u dobitnu kombinaciju.","Dama i lovac na dugoj dijagonali odlučuju.","Dama uzima na f6 — započinje dobitnu kombinaciju."]}', HintsVersion=1 WHERE LineId LIKE '%:012.084' AND BookFileName='chessable-u5-49693.pgn';
UPDATE BookPuzzles SET HintsJson='{"de":["Schwarz hat eine Wendung, die nicht zu parieren ist.","Turm und Läufer opfern sich, dann schlägt der zweite Turm ein.","Turm schlägt auf d1 – beginnt die gewinnende Kombination."],"en":["Black has a blow that cannot be parried.","Rook and bishop sacrifice, then the second rook strikes.","Rook takes on d1 — starting the winning combination."],"hr":["Crni ima udarac koji se ne može odbiti.","Top i lovac se žrtvuju, a onda udara drugi top.","Top uzima na d1 — započinje dobitnu kombinaciju."]}', HintsVersion=1 WHERE LineId LIKE '%:012.085' AND BookFileName='chessable-u5-49693.pgn';
UPDATE BookPuzzles SET HintsJson='{"de":["Schwarz hat eine Opferwendung, die entscheidend durchbricht.","Springer und Dame jagen den weißen König ins Verderben.","Springer schlägt auf h3 – beginnt die gewinnende Kombination."],"en":["Black has a sacrificial blow that breaks through decisively.","Knight and queen drive the white king to its doom.","Knight takes on h3 — starting the winning combination."],"hr":["Crni ima udarac sa žrtvom koji odlučno probija.","Skakač i dama gone bijelog kralja u propast.","Skakač uzima na h3 — započinje dobitnu kombinaciju."]}', HintsVersion=1 WHERE LineId LIKE '%:012.086' AND BookFileName='chessable-u5-49693.pgn';
UPDATE BookPuzzles SET HintsJson='{"de":["Schwarz manövriert den Springer in einen entscheidenden Vorteil.","Springer und Läufer arbeiten gegen die weiße Königsstellung.","Springer nach e4 – beginnt die gewinnende Kombination."],"en":["Black maneuvers the knight to a decisive advantage.","Knight and bishop work against the white king''s defenses.","Knight to e4 — starting the winning combination."],"hr":["Crni manevrira skakača do odlučujuće prednosti.","Skakač i lovac djeluju protiv obrane bijelog kralja.","Skakač na e4 — započinje dobitnu kombinaciju."]}', HintsVersion=1 WHERE LineId LIKE '%:012.087' AND BookFileName='chessable-u5-49693.pgn';
UPDATE BookPuzzles SET HintsJson='{"de":["Schwarz hat einen erzwungenen Matt.","Turm und Dame umstellen den weißen König unausweichlich.","Turm nach f8 – beginnt das erzwungene Matt."],"en":["Black has a forced mate.","Rook and queen surround the white king inescapably.","Rook to f8 — starting the forced mate."],"hr":["Crni ima prisilni mat.","Top i dama neizbježno opkoljavaju bijelog kralja.","Top na f8 — započinje prisilni mat."]}', HintsVersion=1 WHERE LineId LIKE '%:012.088' AND BookFileName='chessable-u5-49693.pgn';
UPDATE BookPuzzles SET HintsJson='{"de":["Schwarz behält trotz Bauernunterzahl die Oberhand.","Der Springer und der eigene König halten die weißen Bauern auf.","Springer nach g6 – beginnt die gewinnende Folge."],"en":["Black keeps the upper hand despite being a pawn down.","The knight and the king together stop the white pawns.","Knight to g6 — starting the winning sequence."],"hr":["Crni zadržava prevagu unatoč manjku pješaka.","Skakač i vlastiti kralj zaustavljaju bijele pješake.","Skakač na g6 — započinje dobitni niz."]}', HintsVersion=1 WHERE LineId LIKE '%:012.089' AND BookFileName='chessable-u5-49693.pgn';
UPDATE BookPuzzles SET HintsJson='{"de":["Ein Läuferopfer reißt die Rochadestellung auf und gewinnt.","Nach dem Opfer dringen Dame und Türme zum König vor.","Läufer schlägt auf h3 – beginnt die gewinnende Kombination."],"en":["A bishop sacrifice rips open the castled position and wins.","After the offer, queen and rooks pour in at the king.","Bishop takes on h3 — starting the winning combination."],"hr":["Žrtva lovca razbija rokiranu poziciju i dobiva.","Nakon žrtve dama i topovi prodiru do kralja.","Lovac uzima na h3 — započinje dobitnu kombinaciju."]}', HintsVersion=1 WHERE LineId LIKE '%:012.090' AND BookFileName='chessable-u5-49693.pgn';
UPDATE BookPuzzles SET HintsJson='{"de":["Ein scharfer Schlag rettet den halben Punkt – nutze den Druck deiner Figuren.","Der Läufer öffnet die Stellung und die schweren Figuren liefern danach den Dauerschach-Mechanismus.","Läufer schlägt auf g2 – beginnt die rettende Kombination."],"en":["A sharp blow secures the half point — exploit your active pieces.","The bishop cracks the position open and the heavy pieces then deliver the perpetual.","Bishop takes on g2 — starting the saving combination."],"hr":["Oštar udarac spašava pola boda — iskoristi aktivne figure.","Lovac otvara poziciju, a teške figure potom drže vječni šah.","Lovac uzima na g2 — započinje spasonosnu kombinaciju."]}', HintsVersion=1 WHERE LineId LIKE '%:012.091' AND BookFileName='chessable-u5-49693.pgn';
UPDATE BookPuzzles SET HintsJson='{"de":["Die weit vorgerückten Bauern entscheiden – ein König-und-Bauern-Endspiel ist gewonnen.","Der König muss vorrücken, damit die Freibauern durchlaufen können.","König nach c5 – leitet die entscheidende Abwicklung ein."],"en":["The far-advanced pawns decide — the king and pawn ending is winning.","The king must step up so the passed pawns can run.","King to c5 — beginning the decisive sequence."],"hr":["Daleko nadirući pješaci odlučuju — pješačka završnica je dobivena.","Kralj mora naprijed kako bi prolazni pješaci protrčali.","Kralj na c5 — pokreće odlučujući slijed."]}', HintsVersion=1 WHERE LineId LIKE '%:012.092' AND BookFileName='chessable-u5-49693.pgn';
UPDATE BookPuzzles SET HintsJson='{"de":["Ein Opfer reißt die Königsstellung auf und gewinnt entscheidend.","Der Turm verschwindet als Köder, damit Dame und Läufer den König erlegen.","Turm schlägt auf e6 – beginnt die gewinnende Kombination."],"en":["A sacrifice tears open the king and wins decisively.","The rook is offered as bait so the queen and bishop can finish the king.","Rook takes on e6 — starting the winning combination."],"hr":["Žrtva razbija kraljevu poziciju i odlučujuće dobiva.","Top se nudi kao mamac da dama i lovac dokrajče kralja.","Top uzima na e6 — započinje dobitnu kombinaciju."]}', HintsVersion=1 WHERE LineId LIKE '%:012.093' AND BookFileName='chessable-u5-49693.pgn';
UPDATE BookPuzzles SET HintsJson='{"de":["Der aktive König und der starke Springer holen entscheidenden Vorteil.","Der König marschiert vor und der Springer sichert das gewonnene Endspiel.","König nach f3 – leitet die gewinnende Folge ein."],"en":["The active king and the strong knight bring a decisive edge.","The king marches forward while the knight clinches the won ending.","King to f3 — beginning the winning sequence."],"hr":["Aktivni kralj i jaki skakač donose odlučujuću prednost.","Kralj nastupa naprijed dok skakač osigurava dobivenu završnicu.","Kralj na f3 — pokreće dobitni slijed."]}', HintsVersion=1 WHERE LineId LIKE '%:012.094' AND BookFileName='chessable-u5-49693.pgn';
UPDATE BookPuzzles SET HintsJson='{"de":["Ein Schlag gegen die Königsstellung leitet einen gewinnenden Angriff ein.","Der Springer opfert sich, damit die schweren Figuren über den König herfallen.","Springer schlägt auf f7 – beginnt die gewinnende Kombination."],"en":["A strike at the king''s shelter launches a winning attack.","The knight sacrifices itself so the heavy pieces can swarm the king.","Knight takes on f7 — starting the winning combination."],"hr":["Udarac po kraljevu zaklonu pokreće dobitni napad.","Skakač se žrtvuje da teške figure nasrnu na kralja.","Skakač uzima na f7 — započinje dobitnu kombinaciju."]}', HintsVersion=1 WHERE LineId LIKE '%:012.095' AND BookFileName='chessable-u5-49693.pgn';
UPDATE BookPuzzles SET HintsJson='{"de":["Ein präziser Bauerntausch ebnet den Weg zum gewonnenen Bauernrennen.","Der Königsflügel wird geklärt, damit der eigene Freibauer schneller läuft.","Bauer nach h5 – beginnt die gewinnende Abwicklung."],"en":["A precise pawn trade clears the path to a winning pawn race.","The kingside is cleared so the own passed pawn runs faster.","Pawn to h5 — beginning the winning sequence."],"hr":["Precizna zamjena pješaka otvara put do dobivene utrke pješaka.","Kraljevo krilo se raščišćava da vlastiti prolazni pješak brže trči.","Pješak na h5 — započinje dobitni slijed."]}', HintsVersion=1 WHERE LineId LIKE '%:012.096' AND BookFileName='chessable-u5-49693.pgn';
UPDATE BookPuzzles SET HintsJson='{"de":["Ein Damenmanöver gewinnt entscheidendes Material.","Die Dame zwingt einen Abtausch, der zu Materialgewinn führt.","Dame nach f3 – beginnt die gewinnende Folge."],"en":["A queen maneuver wins decisive material.","The queen forces an exchange that nets material.","Queen to f3 — beginning the winning sequence."],"hr":["Manevar dame osvaja odlučujući materijal.","Dama prisiljava zamjenu koja donosi materijal.","Dama na f3 — započinje dobitni slijed."]}', HintsVersion=1 WHERE LineId LIKE '%:012.097' AND BookFileName='chessable-u5-49693.pgn';
UPDATE BookPuzzles SET HintsJson='{"de":["Ein Damenvorstoß nahe dem König entfesselt einen gewinnenden Angriff.","Die Dame und der Springer wirken zusammen, um die Königsstellung zu sprengen.","Dame nach h3 – beginnt die gewinnende Kombination."],"en":["A queen thrust near the king unleashes a winning attack.","The queen and knight combine to break open the king''s position.","Queen to h3 — starting the winning combination."],"hr":["Prodor dame uz kralja pokreće dobitni napad.","Dama i skakač zajedno razbijaju kraljevu poziciju.","Dama na h3 — započinje dobitnu kombinaciju."]}', HintsVersion=1 WHERE LineId LIKE '%:012.098' AND BookFileName='chessable-u5-49693.pgn';
UPDATE BookPuzzles SET HintsJson='{"de":["Ein Springeropfer macht den Weg für den eigenen Freibauern frei und gewinnt.","Der Springer räumt einen Verteidiger weg, damit der Bauer durchläuft.","Springer nach c3 – beginnt die gewinnende Abwicklung."],"en":["A knight sacrifice clears the way for the own passer and wins.","The knight removes a defender so the pawn can run through.","Knight to c3 — beginning the winning sequence."],"hr":["Žrtva skakača krči put vlastitom prolaznom pješaku i dobiva.","Skakač uklanja branitelja da pješak protrči.","Skakač na c3 — započinje dobitni slijed."]}', HintsVersion=1 WHERE LineId LIKE '%:012.099' AND BookFileName='chessable-u5-49693.pgn';
UPDATE BookPuzzles SET HintsJson='{"de":["Trotz Mehrfigur sichert genaues Spiel den vollen Vorteil – halte den König aktiv.","Der eigene König muss richtig manövrieren, während die Bauern zählen.","König nach g7 – beginnt die entscheidende Folge."],"en":["Precise play secures the full edge — keep the king active.","The own king must maneuver correctly while the pawns count.","King to g7 — beginning the decisive sequence."],"hr":["Precizna igra osigurava punu prednost — drži kralja aktivnim.","Vlastiti kralj mora pravilno manevrirati dok pješaci odlučuju.","Kralj na g7 — započinje odlučujući slijed."]}', HintsVersion=1 WHERE LineId LIKE '%:012.100' AND BookFileName='chessable-u5-49693.pgn';
UPDATE BookPuzzles SET HintsJson='{"de":["Ein Angriff auf den eingeengten König entscheidet die Partie.","Turm und Dame bündeln ihre Kraft gegen die Königsstellung.","Turm nach g6 – beginnt die gewinnende Kombination."],"en":["An attack on the cramped king decides the game.","Rook and queen pool their force against the king''s position.","Rook to g6 — starting the winning combination."],"hr":["Napad na stiješnjenog kralja odlučuje partiju.","Top i dama udružuju snagu protiv kraljeve pozicije.","Top na g6 — započinje dobitnu kombinaciju."]}', HintsVersion=1 WHERE LineId LIKE '%:012.101' AND BookFileName='chessable-u5-49693.pgn';
UPDATE BookPuzzles SET HintsJson='{"de":["Im Turmendspiel entscheidet ein einziger Tempogewinn zugunsten des Verteidigers.","Der aktive König und der Turm sichern das gewonnene Rennen.","König nach g3 – beginnt die entscheidende Folge."],"en":["In the rook ending a single tempo tips the balance the defender''s way.","The active king and rook clinch the winning race.","King to g3 — beginning the decisive sequence."],"hr":["U topovskoj završnici jedan jedini tempo prelama stvar u korist branitelja.","Aktivni kralj i top osiguravaju dobivenu utrku.","Kralj na g3 — započinje odlučujući slijed."]}', HintsVersion=1 WHERE LineId LIKE '%:012.102' AND BookFileName='chessable-u5-49693.pgn';
