UPDATE BookPuzzles SET HintsJson='{"de":["Schwarz erzwingt das Matt in der Ecke.","Türme und Springer schnüren den weißen König am Rand fest.","Beginne mit dem Turm nach g3 und beginne die erzwungene Folge."],"en":["Black forces mate trapping the king in the corner.","Rooks and a knight pin the white king to the edge.","Start with the rook to g3 to begin the forced line."],"hr":["Crni prisiljava mat u kutu.","Topovi i skakač prikuju bijelog kralja uz rub.","Počni topom na g3 da započneš prisilni niz."]}', HintsVersion=1 WHERE LineId LIKE '%:037.046' AND BookFileName='chessable-u5-243265.pgn';
